Emalunga eMkhandlu WaseWales akafuni 'kufana nema-muppet'
Lamanye emalunga aleSigungu saVelonkhe akasaneliseki ngelucingo lwekutsi emagama awo kumele abhalwe nge-MWP (kusuka kuSiswati Member of the Welsh Parliament  lilunga lePhalamende yase Wales).
Lesincumo lesimatima sihlobene netinhlelo tekugucula ligama leSigungu kutsi libe yiPhalamende yaseWales.
Emalunga eMkhandlu weTifundza laphuma emacenjini epolitiki akhatsateke ngekutsi kungenteka kutsi kunemanga ngalesichazamagama.
Lenye incenye yelicembu le-Labour, iveta kukhatsateka kwayo ngekutsi leligama lelisha lihlehliswe ngekutsi Twp na Pwp.
Kulabangasiwo emaWelsh, twp ngesiWelsh kusho "silima" kantsi pwp kusho "silima".
Ngekusho kwemalunga e-Assembly laphuma e-Welsh Party, inhlangano yakhe "ayigcwali kweneliseka" futsi yacela letinye tindlela.
Lamalunga alelicembu le-Muppet akahambisani naloluhlelo lolusha, kodvwa aphawula kutsi i-MWP isondzelene neligama lelitsi Muppet.
Kulendzaba, leligama lelitsi w ngesiWelsh liphuma cishe njengaleli lelitsi u ngesiNgisi saseYorkshire.
Likomidi le-Assembly, lelisatfutfukise lomtsetfo wekuntjintja ligama, latsi:  Sincumo sekugcina sekutsi emalunga e-Assembly atawubitwa njani, siyasala kubo.
UMtsetfo wekuPhatfwa kweMave aseWales wanga-2017 unikete uMkhandlu waVelonkhe waseWales emandla ekutsi ugucule ligama lawo.
NgaJuni, iKomiti yakhipha imiphumela yeluphenyo lwembono wemphakatsi mayelana naloluhlelo loluphakanyisiwe, lolwaluphakamisa kutsi iPhalamende yaseWales esikhundleni se-Assembly itfole kwesekelwa lokukhulu kubantfu bendzawo.
Mayelana nemagama emalunga e-Assembly, i-Welsh Parliament Members (WMP) yashiwo njengelibito lelisembili lelifanele, kantsi i-MWP yona inekwesekelwa lokukhulu emphakatsini.
Emalunga aleSigungu kumele akhetse lokunye lokungahle kube khona, kepha kutawuba matima kutsi lilunga lelibusako, Elaine Jones, litfole sincumo lesibaniketa injabulo.
Imitsetfo yetingucuko itawufaka ekhatsi letinye tingucuko kumsebenti weSigungu, kufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo lemisha yekungafaneleki kwemalunga eSigungu kanye nekuhlelwa kweluhlelo lweKomidi.
Emalunga aleSigungu atawuvota ngeligama lawo lelingumtsetfosisekelo ngesikhatsi sekuphikisana ngalomtsetfo.
Bantfu baseMacedonia batawuvota ku-referendum yekugucula ligama lelive labo
NgeLisontfo, bantfu baseMacedonia batawuvota kute kutsi lelive libitwe ngekutsi yi "Republic of Northern Macedonia".
Lokuvota kwentiwe kute kucatululwe imphi lesekuphele iminyaka leminyenti inayo neGrisi leyakhelene nayo, lenesifundza sayo iMacedonia.
Hulumende waseGreece usolo utsi ligama lelitsi "Republic of Macedonia" lisho kutsi unetinjongo tekufaka sandla esifundzeni saseGreece, futsi uphindze waphikisana nekungena kwelive lakhona lelingasemnyakatfo ku-European Union kanye ne-NATO.
Mengameli waseMacedonia, George Ivanov, longumphikisi waloluhlelo lwekuhlola, utsi angeke awuvume umphumela waloluhlelo.
Nanobe kunjalo, labo labatsandza lencwadzi, lokufaka ekhatsi Ndvunankhulu Zoran Zaev, batsi kugucula ligama lelive  kumane nje kuyindleko yekujoyina i-EU ne-NATO.
