Kodvwa-ke, lokukhatsatako mayelana nemasontfo kutsi imali levela ekutsengisweni kwemitfombolusito angeke isebente sikhatsi lesidze, ngisho nobe baholi bawo bangatsemba kutsi batawutfola imali lenyenti.
Watsi: "Kutawuvela indlu lenemakamelo lamanyenti endzaweni yeliSontfo, futsi bantfu labakuleyo ndzawo angeke basayisekela lendzawo.
Adams utsi: "Linyenti lebantfu labatsenga letindlu litawuba ngema-White, futsi kutawusondzela lilanga lapho emasontfo lanjalo atawuvalwa khona, ngobe labomakhelwane labasha angeke babe ngemalunga awo.
Lamasontfo lamabili akhiwa ngemabandla ebantfu labamhlophe ngaphambi kwekutsi Harlem ibe tindzawo tebantfu labamnyama: iMetropolitan Community nga 1870, neSanta Martin Church ngemuva kweminyaka lelishumi.
