Lendzawo yabo beyitsengwe libandla lebantfu labamnyama lebebakulo.
Ngesikhatsi lisontfo le St. Martin's selivele lisetandleni tebantfu labamnyama, lelisontfo lacondziswa ngu Reverend John Howard Johnson, lowahlela kuvalwa kwetitolo e 125th Street, lokuyindzawo lenkhulu yekutsengisa eHarlem, lapho bantfu labamnyama bebangavunyelwa khona kutsi basebente nobe batfutfukiswe.
Ngemnyaka wa 1939 ngemuva kwekushiswa kwesakhiwo, lesakhiwo salimala kakhulu, futsi ngesikhatsi sekulungiswa, emabandla a-Father Johnson ayala kutsi kufakwe i-carillon.
