Lwati lwe-University of Michigan, Tiffany Ng, waphindze watsi, le-carillon yaseSt. Martin's Church kwaba yintfo yekucala emhlabeni wonkhe leyayidlalwa ngumuntfu lomnyama, Dionisio A. Lind, lowamenywa eminyakeni lengu-18 leyendlulile kutsi adlale kule-carillon lenkhulu eRiverside Church.
Ngekusho kwaMerriweiser, kute umuntfu losatfole indzawo yakhe esontfweni laseSt. Martin.
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letendlulile, simo lesimatima besikhona mayelana nelibandla leSanta Martin, kanye nebakhi netisebenti, labanye babo bebabitwa baholi belibandla, labanye bebabitwa yi-Episcopal Church.
