Sainsbury uhlela kuhlupha emakethe yetintfo letiphunga kanye naletinye tekuhlobisa yaseBrithani
Sainsbury uhlela kusungula tindzawo tekuhlobisa kanye netinongo kuBoots, Superdrag, kanye naseDebenhams, kanye nebakhulumeli betinongo, njengetindzawo letitsandvwa kakhulu.
Imakethe yetintfo letiphungako yase UK itsatsa imali letigidzigidzi letingu 2.8 futsi iyachubeka nekukhula, kepha imfashini kanye netintfo letititsengiswako ekhaya tiyawa. kute kutsatselwe incenye lenkhulu yalenkhundla lefunwako, titolo letingu-11 kulelive letitawuhlola tibe nemakamelo lamakhulu etintfo letiphungako kanye netintfo letiphungako, futsi uma kuphumelela, titolo letinyenti titawufika kulomnyaka lotako.
Bantfu labatsengisa etitolo letinkhulu bafuna tintfo letingagcwala ema-shelf abo, labake batfola tintfo letingagcwala ema-TV, ema-microwave, tintfo tekutilungiselela, kanye nekutsengisa emarikeli etinongo kanye netintfo tekugcobisa.
Ngekusho kwebameleli be Sainsbury, kuhlelwa kutsi kukhuliswe luhlobo lwetintfo tekuhlobisa ngalokuphindvwe kabili kuya ku-3 000; kufaka ekhatsi, kwekucala ngca kutfolakala emabhrendi lafana ne Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman kanye ne Dr. PawPaw.
Letitolo letisemakethe letingu-L'Oreal, Maybelline kanye ne-Burt's Bees titawufakwa etindzaweni letisetulu, njengetitolo te-Boots.
Ngetulu kwaloko, umkhicito we-boutique-cosmetics utawuhlelwa kabusha, bese ushintshela kumikhicito ye-vegan kute kuhlangabetwane netidzingo tebantfu labasha labatsenga.
Titselo te-Fragrance Shop titawuvulwa kuletitolo letimbili taseSainsbury: yimbi yavula e-Croydon leseNingizimu London ngeliviki leliphelile, bese kutsi yesibili ivule e-Selly Oak lese-Birmingham kulomnyaka.
Kutsengisa nge-Internet kanye nekutsenga lokuncane kakhulu ngelilanga etitolo letincane letisedvute nalapho uhlala khona, sekucindzetele timakethe kutsi tifune kutsenga ngetindlela letinsha.
Mike Coop, umengameli weSainsbury's, utsi ema-outlet atawugucuka abe ngemakethe, kantsi inethiwekhi yakhe yetitolo letinkhulu ilwela emakhasimende ayo, ikhuphisana netitolo letishibhile letifana ne-Aldi ne-Liddle, ngekuniketa tinsita letinyenti kanye netintfo letingekho kudla.
Emakhulu etitolo letinkhulu tase Sainsbury's tinetindzawo tekutsengisela iArgos, kantsi letinye tato nyalo tingatfola tindzawo tekutsengisela iHabitat's kusukela lelicembu latfola lamagama eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, loku kwenta kutsi kukhicitwa kwekudla kanye netimali letitfolwa ngekutsengiswa kwetintfo letitsengiswako tikhule.
Emetamo leyentiwe ngulesigatja kutsi sivuselele tindzawo tekuhlobisa kanye netekutsengisa imitsi ayiphumelelanga.
Ekucaleni kwemnyaka wa 2000 kwakhiwa ibhizinisi lehlangene leyakhiwa yi Sainsbury neBoots, kepha ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi kwaba nekungavumelani emkhatsini walaba labatsintsekako mayelana nekuhlukanisa imali lebuya ekutsengisweni kwetintfo temitsi etitolo letinkhulu.
Lendlela lensha yacalwa ngemuva kwekutsengiswa kwebhizinisi le Sainsbury's leyayinelitolo lelikhulu nemashumi lamabili nesiphohlongo (tindzawo tekutsengisela) ku Selesio, umnikati we-Lloyds Pharmacy, ngemali lengemarandi lalikhulu nemashumi lamabili nesihlanu etingidini eminyakeni lemitsatfu leyengcile.
I-Lloyds kulindzeleke kutsi isekele lelilungiselelo ngekwengeta luhlu lolubanti lwetintfo tekunakekela sikhumba letibitwa ngekutsi yi-La Roche-Posay ne-Vichy kuletitolo letine.
Paul Mills-Hicks, umCondzisi weTekuhweba waseSainsbury utsi: "Sisungule kabusha indlela yekubukeka kanye nemoya wemabhizinisi etfu etinongo nasetintfweni tekugcobisa kute sakhe indzawo lencono yekutsengisa emakhasimende etfu.
Siphindze sacela beluleki labaceceshelwe umsebenti kutsi basite etikhungo.
Umkhicito wetfu lohlanyelwe tonkhe tinhlobo tetintfo, umklamo lomuhle kanye netitolo letitfolakala endzaweni lelula kutawujabulisa tivakashi letinyenti letifuna tintfo tekugcobisa kanye nemakha.
Peter Jones uphendvule ngekutfukutsela ngemuva kwekuphuma kwaHolly Willoughby kumklamo wemali letigidzi leti-11 temarandi.
Peter Jones, inkhanyeti ye-"Logic Dragon", ucasukile ngekutsi umengameli welive Holly Willoughby akashiyi licebo lakhe le-£11 million lekuphilisa naPeter, kodvwa esikhundleni saloko wakhetsa kwenta sivumelwano lesisha naMarks and Spencer kanye ne-ITV.
Willowbie akanaso sikhatsi sekwenta tintfo letihambisana ne-Truly, lokuyimikhiqizo yetimphahla tasekhaya kanye netintfo letisetjentiswa ekhaya.
Lebhizinisi yalaba labashadako beyibutsana neGoop ye-actress Gwyneth Paltrow.
Lomchumanisi loneminyaka lengu-37 budzala waveta sincumo sakhe nga-Instagram ngalelolanga ekuseni.
Sincumo saHolly Willoughby sekushiya lifestyle brand leyayimphumelelisa imali yakhe kute agcine asayine ema-Marx and Spencer kanye ne-ITV, kwabangela kutsi Peter Jones, lobekangumdlali we-Dragon Lies, acansuke kakhulu.
Imibiko lesayitfola kutsi Jones bekatfukutsele kakhulu ngesikhatsi umlingani wakhe labemtsandza kakhulu avuma emhlanganweni lobudzala lowawuse Marlow, eBuckinghamshire, kutsi ngemuva kwekucinisa imiculu lemisha letigidzi letingu-1.5 bekangeke abe nesikhatsi lesenele sekwenta tintfo tabo tekugcoka kanye netintfo tekugcoka.
Loluhlobo lwalo belucatsaniswa neGoop, umntfwana wemlingisi Gwyneth Paltrow, futsi bekulindzeleke kutsi kutsengiswa kwalo kutakwenta umcebo waWilloughby uphindvwe kabili, lobekufanele kutsi ubalwe ngemali letigidzi letingu-11 temali.
Lomchumanisi loneminyaka lengu-37 budzala wamemetela ngekuhamba kwakhe ku-Instagram, kantsi yena Jones washiya i-UK ngemkhumbi wakhe wangasese waya kulelinye lema-villa akhe.
Lomunye wemitfombo utsi iTruly bekungumklamo waHolly.
Bekungukutsengisa sikhatsi lesidze lokwakutawusenta sibe nemphilo lenhle iminyaka leminyenti.
Lesincumo sakhe samangalisa bonkhe labatsintsekako kuloluhlelo.
Bonkhe bantfu bebabambe wangephansi ngaloko lokwenteka ngaLesibili, ngobe bekusele emaviki lambalwa kutsi kube khona lomklamo.
Sisalelwe yindzawo yekubekisa tintfo letitsite letigcwele tintfo letitsengiswako.
Tati tikholelwa kutsi kuhamba kwalona lowetayelekile kakhulu kule-TV, "Lentfombi Lelikhulumela Kusasa" kungatsatsa tigidzi temali ngenca yekutsengiswa kwetintfo letinyenti, kusukela kumaphilisi kuya kumakhandlela kuya etingubo, kanye nekubambezeleka kwekusungula.
Ngetulu kwaloko, kusho kutsi sehlukana nebangani bakho.
Willowbie nendvodza yakhe Dan Baldwin, labanebantfwana labatsatfu, bebanebungani naJohnson kanye nemkakhe Tara Capp, iminyaka lelishumi.
Willowbee wasungula iTruly brand kanye naTara Capp nga-2016, kantsi indvodza yaTara, Peter Jones, loneminyaka lengu-52 budzala, wahola liBhodi leNkampani ngaMashi.
Bobabili laba labashadene bavame kuvakasha ndzawonye, futsi, ngetulu kwaloko, Jones unemasheya langu-40% kuDan Baldwin's Television Production Company.
Willoughby utawuba ngummeli we M&S futsi utawususa Anthony McPartlin esikhundleni sakhe njengemchumanisi we ITV.
Umuntfu lotsite losondzelene na Jones watsi ebusuku itolo: "Asikwati kukhuluma ngetintfo latenta".
Tintfo betimatima, kodvwa besisolo sitsandzana.
