Bantfu labanyenti bebangashona.
Kodvwa nyalo sinebudlelwane lobuhle.
Ngekusho kwaTrump, imitamo yakhe yekulungisa budlelwane naKim Jong-un yaletsa titselo: kwacedvwa kwetfulwa kwetinhlosoma, kwavulwa tigebengu, futsi netisebenti teMelika lebetiseKhongolose nato tabuyela ekhaya.
