Kutamatama kwemhlaba ne-tsunami e-Indonesia: Kulimala lokukhulu, bantfu labanyenti bafile
Ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokwenteka eLombok, ema-NGO angaphandle atjelwa kutsi asidzingi lusito.
Nanobe bantfu labangetulu kwa-10% baseLombok bashiye tindlu tabo, hulumende akazange akubone kunesidzingo sekumemetela inhlekelele yemvelo, lokungumgomo lobalulekile wekutfola lusito lwemave emhlaba.
 Esikhatsini lesinyenti, ngelusizi, bebakwenta kucace kutsi abadzingi lusito lwemave emhlaba, ngako-ke bekungasimelula,  kusho Selina Sambung.
I-Save the Children seyisungula licembu lekutfumela ePalu, kodvwa asati kutsi licembu langaphandle lingakhona yini kusebenta lapho.
Ngekusho kwaSuthupo, lokunguyena ummeleli weLitiko Letekuphepha Letehlakalo, baphatsi base-Indonesia benta luhlolo lwekutsi ngabe kuncono yini kutsi kuhlanganiswe tinhlangano temhlaba.
Ngenca yekungahlaliseki lokungapheli kwemhlaba, live lase-Indonesia lisengakalungiselelwa kahle kuhlangabetana netehlakalo temvelo.
Nanobe kwakhiwe tindzawo tekukhosela ema-tsunami e-Achehe, kodvwa akukavami kutsi tibonwe kulamanye emabhishi.
Nanobe bekunesecwayiso sekugadla kwentsamatseke, i-Palu ayizange ikhiphe imilayeto yekuyala bantfu, lokwabangela kutsi kube netinhlekelele letinyenti.
Kuhamba emkhatsini wetihlenge letinyenti tase-Indonesia kuyinkinga ngisho nasesikhatsini lesikahle.
Tinhlekelele temvelo tenta kube matima kakhulu kusebenta.
Sibhedlela lesitimele lebesibeke e-Lombok kute sisite labo labahlupheke, sesitfunyelwa ePalu, kodvwa indlela leya endzaweni yesehlakalo lesisha itawutsatsa emalanga lamatsatfu.
Mengameli Joko Widodo wenta kuciniswa kwesakhiwonchanti lesidzala sase-Indonesia kwaba yintfo lebalulekile emkhankasweni wakhe wekukhetsa, futsi wasebentisa imali lenyenti ekwenteni imigwaco netitimela tibe ncono.
Nanobe kunjalo, hulumende waMengameli Joco, lobekafuna kubusa sikhatsi lesisha emnyakeni lolandzelako, waba netinkinga tekutfola imali.
Umengameli uphindze agcwale umncele wekutsi wenta kutsi kube nekungevani emkhatsini wemaSulumane lamanyenti ase-Indonesia kanye nebantfu labahlala kuwo.
Bantfu labangetulu kwetinkhulungwane babulawa, futsi labanye labatinkhulungwane balahlekelwa tindlu tabo ngenca yekulwa emkhatsini wemaKhristu nemaSulumane, baphutfumiswa ngemashedeni, ngemicibisholo kanye nangetibhamu.
