Kulalelwa kwelicala laMengameli Brett Kavanaugh eSenate kubukwe bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20
Umbiko waBret Kavanaugh kanye naChristina Blazi Ford, lowetfula simangalo lesitsi Kavanaugh wetama kudlwengula umfati ngemnyaka wa 1980, wajabulisa bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20 ngetiteshi letisitfupha te-TV.
Kulandzela lokwehlukana kwepolitiki lokwacala ngemuva kwekuncunywa kwa Kavanaugh, kwavela umbiko lowesabekako ngeLisihlanu, lapho khona umlingani weRiphabliki Jeff Flake abeka umgomo wekutsi ema-FBI afune kuhlolwa kwetinsolo temmeli wakhe ngeliviki linye.
Ford watsi etinkantolo teKhomishani yeTemtsetfo, uneliciniso lelikhulu lekutsi Kawano, ngesikhatsi adzakiwe, wamhlasela futsi wetama kumehlisa etjwaleni emcimbini wesikolwa.
Kawano waveta imiva yakhe, watsi ucinisile ngalokuphelele kutsi loko akuzange kwenteke.
Ngekusho kwe-Nilsen Research Agency, bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20.4 babukela lemphikiswano ngaLesihlanu.
I-Agency ibuke letindzaba letisemkhatsini letivela ku-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kanye ne-MSNBC.
Imininingwane yetiteshi letitsite, letifana ne PBS, C-SPAN ne Fox Business Network, ayikabi khona.
Ngetulu kwaloko, lizinga le-Nielsen alitsatsi njalo kubuka kubukela bantfu labatsandza kubukela i-TV emsebentini.
Nasi sibonelo: Cabanga ngemalunga emndeni langakagadzi kubukela imidlalo yemidlalo ye-baseball nobe umcimbi wekunikelwa kwemklomelo we-Oscar.
Bantfu labanyenti bebabukela iFox News Channel, lebeyisekela kakhulu kukhetfwa kwaKavana: ema-audience aseSenate, labengemalanga lamanyenti, abuke bantfu labalinganiselwa kutigidzi letingu 5,69 kubantfu labamubukele, kusho i-Nielsen.
Indzawo yesibili  ABC lenebantfu labangu 3,26 million.
I-CBS yaba nebantfu labangu 3,1 million, i-NBC yaba nebantfu labangu 2,94 million, i-MSNBC yaba nebantfu labangu 2,89 million, kantsi i-CNN yaba nebantfu labangu 2,52 million, kubika iNielsen.
Ngemuva kwekuba sekube nemhlangano, bantfu labanyenti bebangasafuni kufundza ngalendzaba.
NgaLesihlanu, bekunendzaba lenkhulu lebeyitsintsa inhlitiyo, lebeyitsintsa Jeff Flake.
Ngemuva kwekutsi losenator wase-Arizona, lobitwa ngekutsi ngumuntfu lobambelele embili emalungeni aseRiphabliki, akhulume ngenhloso yakhe yekusekela Kavanaugh, i-CNN ne-CBS bakhona kutfola kutsi uFlake uhlangabetana nelicembu lebantfu labamgceke kakhulu umsenator ngesikhatsi ahamba aye emhlanganweni we-Legal Committee ngaLesihlanu ekuseni.
Live lalibona kutsi uvala emehlo akhe atfole umutsi lobovu lovela kubomake labatsintsekile ku-CNN.
"Ngimi lapha embikwenu", kwasho lomunye wabo.
Ucabanga kutsi ukhuluma liciniso yini kulelive?
"Emvakwakho, emandla, ngesikhatsi labasikati labanyenti bangenawo emandla, "bebatama kuchaza simo sabo sebesifazane.
Flake waphendvula watsi lihhovisi lakhe selikhiphe sitatimende futsi utawuphendvula ngalendzaba emhlanganweni welikomidi.
Ngemuva kwema-awa lambalwa, likomidi leMtsetfo belisolo lilungiselela kuvuma Kawano kutsi abe lijaji futsi litfumele livoti lakhe eSenate, ngako tonkhe tinhlelo te-TV betibukela lomhlangano.
Kodvwa Flake wabeka umgomo munye - kutsi kube neluphenyo lwe-FBI mayelana nalomuntfu lofuna kukhetfwa ngeliviki lelitako, njengobe bekucinisekiswe yi-Democratic minority.
Flake utsi wagucula umbono wakhe ngekungenela kwemngani wakhe, Chris Koons, losanhlangano yeDemokhrasi.
Wenta sincumo sekugcina ngemuva kwekukhuluma naKuns kanye nalamanye emalunga lamanyenti.
Sincumo saFlake saba nemiphumela lemihle ngobe kwacaca kutsi emaRiphabliki bekangakwati kumvumela Kavanaugh ngaphandle kwekuba aphenye.
Umtsetfo waMengameli Trump, wavula luphenyo lwe-FBI macondzana naKawano.
