Kubambana kwemaphoyisa nemaCatalan ngema-separatist ngaphambi kwemnyaka wekucala wenkhululeko
NgaMgcibelo, umhlangano wetinkhulungwane lebukene nekuphuma kwe-Catalonia eSpain, lowahlukanisa live laba ngemacembu lamabili, wabanjwa eBarcelona, futsi kwavela kungcubutana emkhatsini webantfu labatsandza inkhululeko kanye nemaphoyisa.
Emaphoyisa abesabacindzetela labo lebebafuna inkhululeko, ngesikhatsi labo labebagcoke emaski lamnyama bebatsela emacandza kanye nelitfusi lelimphunga kubogadzi, lokwabangela kutsi kube nelutfuli lolumnyama enkabeni yeBarcelona.
Ngemuva kwekutsi emaphoyisa asebentise imijovo yekubamba sicumbi, imibhikisho yacala kabusha.
Ema-awa lamanyenti, labo lebebafuna inkhululeko bebahlabela batsi: "Singeke sikhohlwe, ngeke sicolele!" kantsi lababebaphikisana nabo bebaphendvula batsi: "Hlala kahle Spain!"
Ngekusho kwemaphephandzaba endzawo, bantfu labalishumi nakune labatsatsa luhlangotsi bayiswa esibhedlela banemanceba lamancane.
Nga-Okthoba 1 emnyakeni lowengcile, kwaba nencwadzi yekuhlola lebeyichaza kutsi iCatalonia itawushiya iSpain. Leyo ncwadzi beyibitwa ngekutsi i-Illégal, kodvwa yaba yintfo lebalulekile kuletishoshovu.
I-Catalonia yavota ngekukhululeka lokukhulu kutsi ivele eSpain, kepha kwaba nekubakhona lokuncane ngenca yekutsi labo lebebaphikisana nekuvela kwalelive bebabandlulula.
Ngekusho kwemitfombo lesemtsetfweni yaseCatalonia, bantfu labangu-1 000 balimala ngesikhatsi emaphoyisa etama kuvimbela kuvota lokuchubekako etindzaweni tekukhetsa.
NgeLesihlanu, emavukelambuso alala endleleni lebeyishiwo kutsi iyahamba, kute avimbele umbhikisho wemaphoyisa aseSpain.
Lomkhombandlela wabanjwa, kodvwa wacondza kulenye indlela.
Narcisse Termes, losebenta ngemagetsi loneminyaka lengu-68 budzala, lowaya emhlanganweni webantfu labatsandza kuhlukana, ahamba nemkakhe, ukhala ngekutsi litsemba lekutsi iCatalonia itawutfola bukhosi selibonakala lingaciniseki.
 Emnyakeni lowengcile, kwenteka lokutsite lokwajabulisa bantfu labanyenti.
Batali bami bakhala ngenca yekujabula, ngobe batfole litfuba lekuvota, kodvwa lamuhla sesitfukutsele kakhulu", kusho yena.
Kulokunye, emacembu aseCatalonia labemele kwehlukana neSpain ancoba lukhetfo lolubalulekile, kodvwa kulomnyaka, emacembu abo alahlekelwa ngulabasekeli bawo, njengobe baholi labanyenti labatiwako balomcimbi babaleka nobe baboshiwe, balindzele kutsi batfolwe enkantolo ngenca yendzima yabo ekuhleleni lenhlolovo kanye nekumemetela inkhululeko.
Hoang Puch, loseminyakeni lengu-42 budzala, losebenta ngemishini, lowabhala lucingo emhlanganweni wekusekela emaphoyisa, watsi lokuphikisana sekuvutfwe kakhulu ngito totimbili tinhlangotsi temphikiswano.
"Kukhona kucindzeteleka", wengeta.
NgeMgcibelo, Oriol Junqueras, longulomunye webaholi labamnyama be-Catalan, losandza kuboshwa ekupheleni kwemnyaka lophelile, waveta kutsi unenhloso yekukhetsa kuba lilunga le-European Parliament emnyakeni lotako.
Utsi: "Kuhlanganyela elukhetfweni lolulandzelako lwePhalamende yaseYurophu njengelincenye lelibekiwe yindlela lekahle yekulahla kulahlekelwa kwemagugu entsandvo yelinyenti kanye nekucindzetelwa ngumbuso waseSpain".
