Umdlalo waDolly Mengi wabangela licembu laGary Holt kutsi lifanane ne-Hibernian, lapho lihlanganyela khona indzawo yesibili.
I-Gerard's beyingakabi nelinani lemidlalo lemincane kule Premier League, futsi ngeLisontfo itawuhlangana ne-Hearts, leyenta iRanger ibe nemaphuzu lasiphohlongo ngemuva.
NgeLesine i-Rangers itawudlala imidlalo ye-Europe League ne-Rapid yase-Austria (eVienna).
Liveingston iyachubeka nekungashayi emdlalweni wayo, seyivele idlale imidlalo lesitfupha futsi seyivele ihlulekile kusukela Holt asusa Kenny Miller esikhundleni sekuba ngumceceshi lomkhulu.
