Scott Robinson wakhona kuphuma emgceni wekuvikela, kepha umgomo wakhe awuzange uphume. Ngemuva kwaloko, Alan Lithgow, umvikeli, ngekunyakata kakhulu, wehluleka kuvimbela ibhola laKag Halkett kutsi lingangeni emgceni.
I-Ranger yase-Australia yavumela ema-Ranger kutsi adlale embili, ngobe beyikulindzele kutsi kube netikhatsi letimatima lapho lomdlalo ungacala kabusha.
Nguloko lokwenta kutsi bangayifezi leligama lebalulekile.
