Ngalesikhatsi, iRanger beyinemandla ekuhola, kodvwa bekungekho muntfu longayihlasela, ngako-ke, umgadzi weligili Liam Kelly bekangakhatsateki.
Sikhatsi sesibili sichubeka ngendlela lefanako, nanobe Kelly kwadzingeka kutsi amelane na-Alfredo Morelos.
Umgadzi we-Ranger's, Allan McGregor, wavala ibhola ku-Scott Pittman, kantsi Lithgow wenta umjaho lomkhulu.
Emagugu abeloku angena njalo ejele lase Livingston, kepha onkhe emacala abedliwa, futsi timbili timangalo lebetibekiwe, sinye bekungukuhunga umgadzi wesikhashana Glenn Middleton, lesinye bekungukudlala ngesandla, betingazange tinakwe.
