Emukelekile Erdogan ngesikhatsi avakashele eKeln
NgaMgcibelo, ngaSeptemba 29, ngesikhatsi baholi baseTurkey nebaseJalimane bahlangana kute badle kudla kwasekuseni, bekunemvula lenhle futsi bobabili baholi bebatsandza kudla.
Bekulilanga lekugcina lekuvakasha kwaMengameli Erdogan eJalimane kute acinise budlelwane emkhatsini wemave lamabili lasebandleni le NATO  kuvakasha, lokwavele kunetimphi.
Baholi bemave behluleka kutfola kuvisisana ngetindzaba letifana nemalungelo eluntfu, inkhululeko yemasiko kanye nekujoyina kweTurkey ku-EU.
Ngemuva kwaloko, Erdogan waya eKöln kute atewubamba lichaza emcimbini wekumemetela lisontfo lelikhulu lelisha.
I-Keln inebantfu labanyenti labaseTurkey labakhona ngaphandle kweTurkey.
Ngenca yetizatfu tekuphepha, emaphoyisa awazange avumele sicumbi sebantfu labati-25 000 kutsi singene esikhungweni semphakatsi, kodvwa bantfu labanyenti labamsekelako Erdogan babeka indzawo eceleni kwentela kubona umengameli wabo.
Kuleyo ndzawo, baphikisi be-Erdogan, lokufaka ekhatsi emaKurd, bahlangana kute balahle yonkhe inchubomgomo ya-Erdogan kanye nesincumo sahulumende waseJalimane sekummemela eJalimane.
Kuba khona kwemibono lephikisanako kulomhlangano kukhombisa kutsi lomuntfu unemibono leminyenti: bantfu labanyenti baseJalimane labanetimphandze taseTurkey bayamhlonipha Erdogan, kantsi labanye bambona njengentamo yekubukela phasi.
