Kuhlukunyetwa ejele laseLong Lartin: Emaphoyisa lasitfupha alimala
Ngekusho kwe-Long Lartin, emaphoyisa lasitfupha alimala ngesikhatsi kunetiphitsiphitsi ejele lelikhulu lemadvodza.
KuLesihlanu, nga-Apreli, emajele lamakhulu ase-Wustershire, e-Long Lartin, e-Australia, ahlangana futsi ahlangana.
Kute kucedvwe loludlame, loluhlanganisa tiboshwa letisiphohlongo letisuka kulelivekati linye, kwabitwa licembu le-Tornado.
Emaphoyisa atfola kulimala lokuncane etinhlavini letilula ebusweni; aniketwa lusito lwetemphilo endzaweni.
Ngekusho kwemuntfu losebenta ejele, basebenti labaceceshelwe ngalokusemtsetfweni bahlanganiswa kute bacedze lesifo ejele laseLong Lartin.
Bantfu labatsatfu kulabantfu labalishumi balahlekelwa yimphilo yabo.
Siyakulahla kusetjentiswa kwemandla etandleni kulesikhungo, futsi kuyacaca kutsi labenti balobubi batawuniketwa emaphoyiseni futsi licala labo lingahle liguculwe sikhatsi lesidze.
I-Long Lartin nyalo inetiboshwa letingetulu kwa-500, letihlanganisa letinye tetigebengu letiyingoti kakhulu kulelive.
NgaJuni, kwatfolakala kutsi umphatsi wejele wabanjwa wahlushwa ngulomunye walabo labebanjwe kabuhlungu.
Nga-October, baphatsi bejele baphocelelwa kutsi baletse emacembu lanetinhloso letitsite kute batfutfukise tiboshwa lebetitfukutsele, lebetigwaza emabhola emagiya kubogadzi.
Sichwaga Rosa singagcwala eFenix, Las Vegas naseSalt Lake City (lokungaba lusito etindzaweni letomile)
Arizona ayivami kuba netiphepho letinemandla, kodvwa kuloku, inenhlanhla: Ekucaleni kweliviki lelitako, lesiphepho lesinguRose, lesitawube sesente umehluko wekugcina, sitawuhamba endzaweni leseNingizimu-nshonalanga, futsi sitawubangela tikhukhula letinkhulu.
I-National Weather Service seyivele icwayise ngetingoti tekutfukutsela lokukhulu ngeMsombuluko nangoLesibili eWestern Arizona, eningizimu neNevada, eningizimu-mpumalanga yeCalifornia kanye nase Utah, kufaka ekhatsi emadolobha lafana nePhoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas kanye neSalt Lake City.
Sichwaga Rosa silindzelwe kutsi sihambe ngendlela lecondzile ngetulu kwePhoenix ngaLesibili bese sifika ngeLisontfo kusihlwa.
I-National Weather Service yase Phoenix yatfumela umbiko ku-Twitter lotsi, kusukela nga-1950 sekube netinhlekelele letingu-10 letisolo tifaka ekhatsi tiphepho letingaphansi kwemakhilomitha langu-320.
Siphepho Katrina (nga-1967) sahlasela 65 km kusuka emnyeleni wase Arizona.
Ngekusho kwetibikezelo tekugcina te-National Meteorological Service, kutawubandza lisentimitha linye kuya kulelishumi, kuletinye tindzawo litawubandza lisentimitha linye esigodzini sase-Arizona.
Letinye tindzawo letisemaphandleni eNingizimu-Nshonalanga, njengase Central Rocky Mountains nase Big Basin, kungahle kube netimvula letingaba ngu 2,55 cm, letinye tindzawo tingaba ngu 10 cm.
Etindzaweni letingenwe ngulesiphepho, imvula leletfwa ngu-Hurricane Rosa ingaba sibusiso ngobe lesifundza sesinesikhatsi lesidze sinesomiso.
Nanobe tikhukhula letinkhulu tingaba yingoti, imvula lenkhulu ingenta kutsi kube ncono ngesikhatsi lesomile, lesingakavami eSouthwest yaseMelika.
Ngekusho kwe-U.S. Drought Monitor, ngetulu kwa-40% we-Arizona unesomiso lesikhulu (sigaba sesibili lesimatima) ,  kubika i-website ye-weather.com.
Sicupho lesibitwa ngekutsi ngu-Hurricane Rosa sitawucala sihlasele live lase-Baja California, eMexico.
NgeLisontfo ekuseni, lesiphepho lesinelicophelo lelisetulu lelingemakhilomitha langu-137 ngelihora, besisendzaweni lengemakhilomitha langu-360 eningizimu yelidolobha lasePunta-Euhenia (Mexico) futsi besisendleleni leya enyakatfo ngesivinini lesingu-19 ngelihora.
Lesiphepho sesibekwe endzaweni lenemanti labandzako elugwini lwe Pacific, ngako-ke siyaphelelwa ngemandla.
Lendzawo itawufika eMexico ngalomhla.
Kutawubakhona tikhukhula kanye netimvula letinkhulu etindzaweni letitsite eMexico.
Esigodzini lesisuka e-Lower California kuya enyakatfo-nshonalanga ye-Sonora, kungahle kwehle imvula lengaba ngemasentimitha langu-710, ngaletinye tindzawo ingaba ngemasentimitha langu-25,  kubika i-website ye-weather.com.
Ngemuva kwaloko, lesiphepho sitawuya enyakatfo, sidzabule eMexico bese sifika esifundzeni sase-Arizona ekuseni kakhulu ngaLesibili, sivele sifike eningizimu ye-Utah ngeLesibili kusihlwa.
Ingoti lenkhulu lesemkhatsini weSiphepho Rosa kanye netinsalela taso, yintfo lehlobene netimvula letinkhulu eCalifornia leseNingizimu, enyakatfo-nshonalanga yeSonora kanye nasetindzaweni letisemaphandleni eningizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika,  kusho iNational Meteorological Service.
Kulindzelwe kutsi letindzawo titawuba netikhukhula letingaba yingoti, kube netigodzi letinemathambo etintsabeni.
