Kutamatama kwemhlaba e-Indonesia kubulale bantfu labanyenti, kantsi linani lebantfu labafile liyachubeka nekukhula
NgaMgcibelo, tiphatsimandla tase-Indonesia tatsi bantfu labangu-384 bafile, labanyenti babo bashaywa ngemagagasi lamakhulu lasogwini lwesichingi sase-Indonesia i-Sulawesi, lapho kwavela khona kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami.
Bantfu bekucala lababulawa ngulesifo bekungemakhulu ebantfu lebebavakashele umkhosi waselwandle ePalu, lokwabangela kutsi emagagasi langemamitha lasitfupha agcwale elwandle ngeLesihlanu nakushona lilanga, ashayisa bonkhe bantfu labebakhona.
Kwaba nenhlekelele yemhlaba lenemandla langetulu kwa-7.5 esigabeni saRichter.
Ngesikhatsi sekuvikelwa kwesiphepho, bantfu bachubeka nekuphumula elwandle esikhundleni sekubaleka bayohlala khona, futsi balahlekelwa yimphilo yabo,  kusho Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, lokhulumela litiko le-Indonesia le-National Disaster Management, emhlanganweni wetintsatseli eJakarta.
 Tsunami ayizange ivele, emanti abenemoto, tigodvo, tindlu letinkhulu, kwabhubhisa konkhe lokwakusendleleni yayo,  kuchaza Nugraho, wengeta ngekutsi i-tsunami yewela lwandle ngesivinini lesingu-497 km/h futsi yawela elugwini ngemandla lamakhulu.
Labanye labakhona bakhuphukela etihlahleni, futsi loko kwasindzisa kuphila kwabo.
Bantfu labangu-16,700 basuka endzaweni lebebahlala kuyo baya etindzaweni tekukhosela letingu-24 ePalu.
Titfombe letitsatswe ngumoya tibonisa tindlu letibhidlikile, emashende, emabhuloho labhidlikile kanye nemasontfo lagcwele emanti.
NgaMgcibelo, lelidolobha leliselwandle belisazamazama.
Kuhlaselwa lokunyenti kwavela endzaweni lenebantfu labangu-2,4 wetigidzi.
Umbiko we-Indonesia's Technology Assessment and Utilization Agency (BPPT) utsi lokutamatama kwemhlaba kwabangela kukhululeka kwemandla lokungaba ngemaphindvwe langu-200 kunekudvuma kwebhomu le-athomu lelahlekisa iHiroshima.
Kungenteka kutsi lomkhukhula waba nemandla kakhulu kunaloko bekulindzelekile ngenca yesimo selidolobha lelisekugcineni kweligede lelidze.
Nughroho wabita lomonakalo ngekutsi "ngumonakalo lomkhulu", watsi tindlu letinkhulungwane, tibhedlela, tindzawo tekutsengisela kanye nemahhotela kwabhidlitwa.
Timbumbi tebantfu labafa tatfolakala ngaphansi kwaletakhiwo letatibhidlikile; bantfu labangu-540 balimala, futsi labanye labangu-29 babitwa ngekutsi bayanyamalala.
Ngroho wengeta kutsi kubulawa nekubhujiswa kwemhlaba kungaba kukhulu kakhulu elugwini lolungaba ngemakhilomitha langu-300 kusuka ePalu, endzaweni yase Dungala, leyatfolakala idvute nendzawo yekuhlaselwa.
Imibiko levela kuDungal "yayicedvwe ngalokuphelele, kute lokwatiko lokwatfolakala".
"Kute bantfu labangetulu kwetinkhulungwane letingu-300" endzaweni yaseDungalo, kusho i-International Committee of the Red Cross, lebasebenti bayo kanye nemavolontiya sebatfutsele kulendzawo lenentfutfuko.
"Kube nenhlekelele, kodvwa loko akusiko kuphela", kusho umbiko.
NgaMgcibelo, i-SAMC yagcwala kugcwala kugceka ngekungakhombisi kutsi i-tsunami seyifikile ePalu, kepha i-SAMC ikholelwa kutsi lamagagasi afike elugwini ngesikhatsi lesicwayiso sekucala sisasebenta.
I-video levela ku-social media iveta indvodza lehlala etulu esakhiweni imemeta kutsi kutawugcwala tsunami, itama kudvonsela bantfu engcondvweni.
