I-USA idzinga kucedza imali yekuhlela i-AI ngalokuphindvwe kabili
Li Kaifu, lositsintsekako nalosomabhizinisi ku-AI, lowatiwa ngekutsi nguGoogle, Microsoft kanye ne-Apple, utsi:  I-US kumele iphindvwe kabili kutinsita tayo kutesayensi.
Kucala, emalunga lamanyenti aseMelika akhulume ngekusebenta nge-AI, kepha eMelika lonkhe kute indlela lecacile yekusebenta nge-AI.
Ngasona lesikhatsi, iChina yetfula luhlelo lwayo lwangemnyaka lowengcile, lolunemgomo wekutsi ibe yincenye yekucala kutemfundvo nge-AI nga-2030.
Li utsi: "Kuphindvwa kabili kwetimali tekucwaninga nge-AI kungaba sicalo lesihle, ngobe emave lamanye asele ngemuva kweMelika, futsi silindzele inchubekela embili ku-AI".
Li utsite ku CNBC kulokwengca kwetimali kungenta kutsi kube matima kakhulu kutsi inchubekelembili lenkhulu ye-AI yentiwe eMelika.
Li, incwadzi yakhe letsi "Inhlanganisela Yekuhlakanipha: I-China, iSilicon Valley kanye neLuhlelo Lwemhlaba Lomusha" leshicilelwe ngenyanga ngu-Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, ungumholi we Sinovation Ventures, lebeyitsenge kuyinye yetinkampani te-AI letinkhulu eChina, i-Face++.
Ngemnyaka wa 1980 eKarnegi Mellon University, wasebenta ngendlela yekuhlakanipha lokwentiwe ngemshini lokwacedza umlingani lomkhulu wase America, Otelo, wase uba ngumholi we Microsoft Research kanye nemengameli we Google eChina.
Lee wakhuluma ngemincintiswano leyake yaba khona yahulumende waseMelika, lefaka ekhatsi i-Defense Advanced Research Projects' Robotics Challenge, wabuta kutsi kutawuphindze kube khona nini umncintiswano lolandzelako kute kutfolakale bantfu labangacabangi ngendlela lefana neyebantfu.
Li utsi bacwaningi baseMelika bavame kusebenta kamatima kute batfole imali yekusekela hulumende.
Li utsi: "Kute bantfu labafundza etikolweni labatsintsekako, kodvwa emabhizinisi".
Emabhizinisi lafana ne Facebook, ne Google kanye nalamanye emacembu etetheknoloji, eminyakeni leyengcile, asebente bantfu labadvumile labasuka etikolweni kute basebente kubuhlakani lobentiwe.
Li ukholelwa kutsi kugucuka kwemitsetfo yetekufika kungasita iMelika ekutfutfukiseni tebuciko.
"Ngicabanga kutsi emakhadi laluhlata kumele avame kuniketwa bantfu labafuna umsebenti kubuhlakani lobentiwe ngemshini", washo.
NgaJulayi 2017, Umkhandlu Wembuso waseChina wakhipha luhlelo lwekusungula butsakatsaka lobusha lobubonakalako.
Li utsi iNational Science Foundation yase China iniketa bososayensi imali ngendlela lefanako naleyo iNational Science Foundation naletinye tinhlangano tahulumende tinika ngayo bososayensi baseMelika imali, kodvwa lizinga lemsebenti wabo lososayensi eChina liphansi.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, litiko letekuvikela laseMelika lavula sikhungo lesihlangene setekuhlakanipha lokwentiwe ngelizinga lelisetulu, lesitawufaka ekhatsi basebenti labasemkhakheni wetekulima kanye newetesayensi, kantsi neNdlu Lemhlophe yamemetela kutsi kutawubekwa ikomidi lelikhetsekile lelihlola ngelizinga lelisetulu.
