Bantfu baseMacedonia bavota ngekuhlola kutsi ngabe kufanele yini kutsi lelive lishintje ligama lalo
Bantfu baseMacedonia ngeLisontfo bavota ngekuhlola kutsi ngabe lelive labo kufanele lishintje ligama libe yi "Republic of North Macedonia" (iRiphabhulikhi yaseNyakatfo yeMacedonia) kute kucatululwe imphi yabo yeminyaka leminyenti neGrisi lebeyivimbela emave abo kutsi angenele i-European Union kanye ne-NATO.
IGrisi, lephindze ibe nelidolobha lelikhulu le-Macedonia, itsi ligama lalelive lelingasemnyakatfo limele indzawo yayo, futsi ivimbele lelive kutsi lingene e-NATO nase-EU.
NgaJuni, bohulumende bobabili bavumelana ngesincumo sekwetsiwa kweligama lelisha, kepha labaphikisako labatsandza sive batsi lolushintjo belutawulimata buve beSlavonic.
Mengameli Georgi Ivanov watsi angeke avote kuloluhlelo, futsi lomkhankhaso wekubandlulula wafaka umbuto wekutsi ngabe bantfu labangu-50% batawuvota yini.
Umbuto lowabutwa kuloluhlolo lwentsandvo yelinyenti wawutsi:  Uyawufuna yini kuba lilunga le-NATO ne-EU uma ngabe kucinisekiswa kutsi kutawuba nesivumelwano neGreece?
Labo labatsandza kugucula leligama, kufaka ekhatsi Ndvunankhulu Zoran Zaev, batsi iMacedonia, lelinye lalamave lavela ngemuva kwekwehlukana kweYugoslavia, kufanele ikhokhe lenhlawulo yekujoyina tinhlangano letifana ne-EU ne-NATO.
"Ngilapha lamuhla kute ngivotele likusasa lelive, kute bantfu labasha baseMacedonia baphile ngekukhululeka ngaphasi kweluhlelo lwe-European Union, ngobe loko kusho imphilo lephephile kitsi sonkhe", kusho Olivera Georgievska, loneminyaka lengu-79, lohlala eSkopje.
Emalunga lemelene nalelive avume kutsi atawuhlonipha imiphumela yaloluhlolo kute kube ngulolucinile, nanobe ingasebenti.
Kugucula leligama kutawudzinga emavoti lamakhulu langulokubili kulokutsatfu kwemalunga ePhalamende.
LiKhomishani leluKhetfo lweluhlelo lwekuVikelwa kweMphakatsi (i-NEC) litsi kute umbiko wekungakhoni kusebenta lokwentiwe ngensimbi yelishumi nakunye.
Kodvwa-ke, bantfu labangu-16% kuphela labaya bavota, nakucatsaniswa nelinani labangu-34% lebebakhona elukhetfweni lolwakamuva lwema-2016, ngesikhatsi bantfu labangu-66% labebabhalisile bavota.
"Ngivotele bantfwana bami, indzawo yetfu eYurophu", kusho Josse Tanewski, loneminyaka lengu-62 budzala, lokhetfwa njengelungu le-Skopje.
Ndvunankhulu waseMacedonia, Zoran Zaev, umkakhe, Zorica kanye nendvodzana yakhe, Dusko, bavotele kuvota eMacedonia mayelana nekuguculwa kwelibito lelive, lokuvula indlela yekujoyina iNATO kanye ne-European Union, eStrumice, eMacedonia, ngamhlaka 30 Septemba 2018.
Wodlamini Kavardarkov, loneminyaka lengu-54, walungisa indzawo lencane embikwenkhundla yePhalamende eSkopje, wabeka titulo embikwetintente letasungulwa takhamiti lebetitawuvala lenkhundla.
"Sifuna kuba sembutfweni weNATO kanye ne-EU, kodvwa sifuna kuhlangana ngenhloko lephakanyisiwe, hhayi ngekusebenta emakamelweni ebantfu", kusho Kavadarkov.
Yebo, singemave laphuyile, kodvwa natsi sinesizotsa.
Uma bangafuni kusemukela njengeMasedoniya, singaya kulamanye emave lafana neChina neRussia, bese siba yincenye ye-Euro-Asia.
Ndvunankhulu Zaev utsi kuba lilunga le NATO kutawuletsa imali eMacedonia, ledzingeka kakhulu kulelive lelinelinani lelisetulu lelisebenti.
"Ngikholwa kutsi linyenti lelikhulu litawuvuma ngobe ngetulu kwa-80% wetakhamiti tetfu tiyayisekela i-EU ne-NATO", kusho Zaev ngemuva kwekuvota.
Ucabanga kutsi imphendvulo lecinisile itawuba "siciniseko sekusasa letfu lelihle".
Luhlolo lolushicilelwe ngeMsombuluko weNhlangano yeTemicimbi Yetembusave yaseMacedonia, lukhombisa kutsi emkhatsini wa-30% na-43% webantfu batawutsatsa luhlangotsi kuloluhlolo, kepha loko kungaphasi kwemandla labekiwe.
Kulomunye umbuto lowentiwe yinchungechunge ye-Telecom-TV yaseMacedonia, kwatfolakala kutsi emaphesenti langu-57 ebantfu labatiphendvulile ahlela kuvota ngeLisontfo.
Emaphesenti langu-70 alabo labatsintsekako atsi batawuvota ngalokulungile.
Kute kube nenkhombandlela, bantfu labangu-50% kanye nalelinye livoti kufanele babe khona.
