John Edward: Lwati lwetilwimi lubaluleke kakhulu kubantfu bemhlaba
Tikolwa letizimele taseScotland tichubeka nelisiko lekufundzisa kahle, loku kwaphindze kwacinisekiswa nga-2018: imiphumela lemihle yetihlolwa ikhombisa kuphumelela kwebantfu ngamunye kanye nelicembu kutemidlalo, tebuciko, temculo kanye naletinye tifundvo letibalulekile emphakatsini.
Letikolo tiyincenye yeLibhodi Letikolwa Letitimele taseScotland (SCIS), lelinebafundzi labangetulu kwa-30 000 eScotland yonkhe, futsi tihlose kufundzisa bafundzi nebatali babo ngetindlela letisezingeni lelisetulu.
Tikolwa letitimele tifuna kucecesha bafundzi babo kutsi batfole imfundvo lephakeme, bakwati kwenta umsebenti wabo, futsi babe takhamuti temhlaba.
Njengencenye yemkhakha wetemfundvo, lonemtfwalo wekusungula nekusebentisa luhlelo lwetikolo, siyabona kutsi tilwimi tesimanje tiyachubeka nekuba tifundvo letibaluleke kakhulu futsi letifunwa kakhulu etikolweni.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, usuke umcela kutsi asebentise ingcondvo yakhe.
Nangabe ukhuluma naye ngelulwimi lwakhe, usuke umtsintsa inhlitiyo.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi singeke setsembele elulwimini lwesiNgisi kuphela uma sifuna kwakha budlelwane nekwetsemba bantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngekubuka imiphumela yekuhlola kwalomnyaka, sibona kutsi tilwimi tihola kakhulu kumazinga ekuhlola futsi tinemamaki laphezulu kakhulu etikolweni letitimele.
Sekukonke, bafundzi labangu-68% labafundza tilwimi tangaphandle batfola silinganiso lesiphakeme se-A.
Imininingwane leyatfolwa etikolweni letingu-74 letingumalunga e-SCIS, yaveta kutsi emaphesenti langu-72 ebantfwana bafundza i-A ngesiMandarin (lokusho siShayina), kantsi emaphesenti langu-72 ebantfu labafundza siJalimane, emaphesenti langu-69 ebantfu labafundza siFulentji, kanye nemaphesenti langu-63 ebantfu labafundza siSpanish nawo atfola i-A.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi etikolweni letitimele eScotland, tilwimi tangaphandle tibonakala tibalulekile kubantfwana nakubantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Lamuhla tifundvo telulwimi tifunwa kakhulu njengetayensi yemvelo, tebuchwepheshe, te-engineering netematiki etikolweni letitimele kanye nakuletinye tikhungo temfundvo.
Luhlolo lolwentiwe yiKhomishini yeTemisebenti nemaKhono yaseBrithani nga-2014 lwaveta kutsi 17 ekhulwini kwetintfo letibangela kutsi bacashi bakutfole kumatima kuhlanganisa bantfu labasebenta etindzaweni letisemsebentini, kungukutsi bete emakhono elulwimi.
Ngaloko-ke emakhono elulwimi ayintfo lebalulekile kute bantfu labasha baphumelele emsebentini wabo.
Njengobe imisebenti leminyenti idzinga lwati lwetilwimi, lamakhono ayadzingeka eveni leligcwele kuhlangana.
Ngisho nobe umfundzi angatsandza kwenta muphi umsebenti, kufundza lulwimi lwesibili kutawumzuzisa kakhulu ngekumfundzisa lolunye lwati lolutawumzuzisa kuphila kwakhe konkhe.
Kukwati kukhuluma nebantfu bakulamanye emave ngekushesha kunika umuntfu lowati tilwimi letinyenti, emandla ekuncintisana.
Ngekusho kweluphenyo lwe-YouGov lwanga-2013 lolwentiwe kubantfu labadzala labangetulu kwa-4000 base-UK, emaphesenti langu-75 alabo bantfu abakwati kukhuluma lulwimi lolwengetiwe kahle ngalokwenele kute basekele inkhulumo, kantsi siFulentji sikuphela kwelulwimi lolunetinombolo letimbili  lesilulwimi lolukhulunywa ngu-15% webantfu labaphendvulwe.
Ngiko nje kubalulekile kutsi sitsatse tinyatselo tekufundzisa ngelulwimi.
Kumunya tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati kuletinye temnotfo losatfutfuka, kutawenta bantfwana bakhone kutfola imisebenti lemihle.
Tikolwa taseScotland tifundzisa tilwimi letehlukene  ngasinye sikolwa sineluhlu lwetilwimi.
Letinye tikolwa tigcila ngetilwimi tesimanje letisemkhatsini, kantsi letinye tifundzisa tilwimi letibaluleke kakhulu eBrithani ngekubuka kutfutfuka kwelive letako nga-2020  njengesiMandarin noma siJapane.
Ngisho nobe ngabe umntfwana wakho unetintfo letijabulisako, tikolwa letitimele titawufundza tilwimi letinyenti, futsi tifundziswa bantfu labanelikhono kuletilwimi.
Tikolwa letizimele taseScotland tifuna kwakha indzawo yekufundza letawulungiselela bantfwana futsi ibaphe emakhono labadzingako kute baphumelele, nobe ngabe likusasa labo linjani.
Kulesikhatsi sanyalo, angeke kuphikwe kutsi etindzaweni temabhizinisi emhlaba wonkhe tilwimi tisasebenta kakhulu ekutfutfukiseni live esikhatsini lesitako, ngako-ke loku kumele kubonakale kahle emfundvweni.
Empeleni tilwimi talamuhla kufanele tibukwe njengetindlela tekuchumana nemave emhlaba.
Tikolwa letizimele titawuchubeka tinikete loluhlelo lolunemehluko kanye netinzuzo kubantfu labasha baseScotland.
