Kulindzela kwebantfu kutsi babone LeBron James enta umsebenti wakhe wekucala e-Los Angeles Lakers sekusondzele ekugcineni.
Lomunye umceceshi wema-Lakers, Luke Walton, umemetele kutsi James utawudlala umdlalo we-Nuggets eSan Diego ngeLisontfo.
Kodvwa kusetawubonakala kutsi utawusicitsa sikhatsi lesingakanani.
"Lokungaphezu kweyodwa futsi lokungaphansi kwemashumi lamane nesiphohlongo", kuphendvula Walton ku-website ye-Lakers.
Mike Trudeau, longumtfumeli we-Lakers, watfumela umbiko ku-Twitter watsi James kungenteka kutsi utawudlala sikhashana.
Ngemuva kwekucecesha kwekucala kweliviki, James wabutwa ngemalungiselelo akhe emidlalo lesitfupha ye-Lakers.
"Ngekuya kwesikhatsi lengikuso, angidzingi imidlalo yangaphambi kwesikhatsi sekuhlela umnyaka", kuphendvula lomdlali.
Umjaho waTrump eNshonalanga yeVirginia, siteshi se-YouTube
Mengameli Donald Trump ucala umhlangano wekukhetsa bantfu lamuhla kusihlwa e Wheeling, eWest Virginia.
Lona ngumhlangano wekucala kulabasihlanu labatawutihlanganisa naTrump evikini lelitako, lokufaka ekhatsi kuvakashela kwakhe emaveni lanemusa aseTennessee naseMississippi.
Njengobe kuvotelwa kwakhe kutsi abe ngumengameli wemajaji aphakeme sekubekelwe eceleni, Trump ufuna kutfola kwesekelwa elukhetfweni lolutawuba khona, ngobe emaRiphabliki angahle alahlekelwe kulawula kweSigungu uma ngabe kuvotelwa kwenteka ngeLweti.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi lesitawuba khona umhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia lamuhla ntsambama, futsi ungawubuka njani ku-inthanethi?
Umhlangano waTrump utawuba seWilling, eWest Virginia, nga-19:00 ntsambama, ngelilanga le-Eastern Time, ngaMgcibelo, September 29, 2018.
Ungamukela umhlangano waTrump ne-West Virginia nge-inthanethi ngekubukhoma ku-YouTube.
Trump kungenteka akhulume kuleliviki mayelana nekukhetfwa kwaBret Kavanaugh kutsi abe lijaji lelikhulu. Lokukhetfwa kwaTrump kwabangela kuphikisana lokukhulu, njengoba Kavanaugh abekwe licala lekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi, futsi kuvotelwa lokwakufanele kwentiwe yiSenate sekuhleli liviki linye, ngesikhatsi i-FBI icwaninga.
Kodvwa injongo lenkhulu yalomkhankhaso kutsi kusite emaRiphabhulikhi kutsi akhulise lizinga lekukhetsa.
Umkhankaso waMengameli Trump wenta kutsi lemitsetfo lesihlanu letawuba khona evikini lelitako isite ekuvuseleleni tisebenti tevolontiya kanye nebasekeli njengoba emaRiphabliki etama kuvikela nekukhulisa linani lawo lelisetulu eSenate naseNdlini yeTiphatsimandla, kusho iReuters.
"Kulawula iCongress kubalulekile eluhlelweni lwayo, ngako-ke umengameli kumele avakashele emave lamanyenti njengobe singena esikhatsini sekukhankasela", kusho umkhulumeli welukhetfo lwa Trump, lowala kubhala ligama lakhe, kubika iReuters.
Lomcimbi lohlelelwe lamuhla eWesbanco Arena e Wheeling, e-Ohio, ePennsylvania, ungaletsa bantfu labatsite labatawubukela lomcimbi, futsi utawudvweba emaphephandzaba asePittsburgh, kusho i-West Virginia Metro News.
Kuvakasha kwaTrump eNshonalanga yeVirginia ngeMgcibelo, kungekucala kutsi avakashele lesigodzi ngenyanga lendlulile, ngobe ngulona live latfola emaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 emphumelelo kulo nga-2016.
Trump wetama kusita Patrick Morrissey, umlingani wakhe wase-West Virginia, losembili emaphikweni ekuvota.
Lokutsi uMorriss angahle abe ngembili kwebantfu labamphikisako, kusho kutsi umengameli kumele abe khona  akusiso sibonakaliso lesihle kuMorriss,  kusho Simon Heder, losati setembusave eWestern Virginia University (licaphunwe yiReuters).
INdebe yeRyder 2018: Licembu laseMelika libonisa kutsi lilungele kulwa futsi linematsemba, litawubanjwa ngeLisontfo
Ngemuva kwemihlangano lemitsatfu leyehlukene, umdlalo waMgcibelo wekubamba umdlandla, kungaba nguloko lokudzingwa yiRyder Cup.
Umklamo wekuntjintja  ngumcondvo lohlukile lowetfulwe etemidlalo, kepha ngulapho badlali bakholwa khona, futsi ukhonjiswa kakhulu kulemincintiswano.
Ngubani-ke lona lowenta lomsebenti?
"Bebanemaphuzu lasitfupha, manje sebane, ngako-ke, ngicabanga kutsi loku kusinyatselo lesincane", kwasho Jordan Spit nakaphuma.
Yebo, ema-Europe anetinhla letine, futsi kunalamanye langu-12 lasengotini.
Bantfu baseMelika, Spit utsi, bayabona umoya, futsi banetizatfu tekutsi bahlale baphilile, hhayi lokuncane nje, ngenca yemfomu yaSpit naJustin Thomas, labadlala ndzawonye lilanga lonkhe, futsi ngamunye wabo angadlala ngemaphuzu lamatsatfu kulalamane.
Sipit bekangumuntfu lonelutsandvo, futsi bekenta tintfo letinhle.
Imibuto yekuncoba yacala kukhula njengobe lomdlalo uchubeka, wavala lomdlalo ngesikhatsi yena naThomas balahlekelwa ngemidlalo lemibili.
Umdlalo wakhe lowaba nemphumelelo emgodzini we-15, wahlangabetana nekuhlatjwa lokufanako, lokusho kutsi bekakholelwa kutsi likilabhu laseMelika linematfuba.
"Kufanele ufune kuhlanganisa emandla akho onkhe futsi unake kakhulu umdlalo wakho", kusho Spit.
Nguloko kuphela lokusele kubadlali.
Kwenta 18 wemigodzi bese siyincoba.
Emadvodza lamabili kuphela labeke atfola emaphuzu lamanyenti kuletinsuku letimbili letendlulile kunaSpit naThomas nguFrancesco Molinari naTommy Fleetwood, labadlala indzima lemcoka emlandvweni weRyder Cup.
Labashadikazi labamangalisako baseYurophu bakhipha labane, futsi kubonakala shengatsi abakwati kwenta emaphutsa.
BoMollywood ngibo kuphela labangazange babambe tithico tabo ngeMgcibelo ntsambama, kodvwa baphindze babalekela tithico tabo ngeMgcibelo ekuseni, ngeLesihlanu ntsambama, futsi nangeliSontfo ekuseni.
Loluhlelo kanye nendlela lebasebenta ngayo, kanye nebasekeli labakhukhumele, kucinisa kukholwa kutsi angeke baphumelele ngeLisontfo, nekutsi nakushona lilanga, kute umgadli lodvumile lotawuba nemandla ekuwina i-Europe kunaFlitwood nobe Molinari.
Bekungaba kuhle kutsi bobabili bebeloku basemigedzeni leyehlukene.
Kodvwa-ke, kusengembili kakhulu kukhuluma ngebuhle beYurophu.
Bubba Watson naWeb Simpson basheshe babulala Sergio Garcia, lobekangumdlali wemidlalo yasekuseni, ngesikhatsi ahlangana na-Alex Noren.
Ema boggs nema boggs lamabili labekadze asebenta emgodzini wekucala, bakha lomSpanish nalomSweden, futsi abazange bakhone kuphuma.
Ngako-ke ngeLisontfo kute umuntfu lotakusita kutsi uphume kulomgodzi.
Kujabulisa kakhulu kubukela umdlalo wemabhola lamane kanye nebadlali labane ngenca yekubambisana emkhatsini walabadlali, kanye neteluleko labaticocela tona, kodvwa bona ngekutimisela bangati, kanye nekutsi lisu labo lingagucuka kanjani ngekushesha.
Kuze kube ngunyalo, iYurophu beyisolo idlala kahle njengelicembu, futsi beyisolo ikhula ngemandla ngelilanga lekugcina, kepha lomdlalo welicembu lelishumi wabuye wakhombisa kutsi licembu laseMelika linemandla ekulwa, lokuyintfo labanye, ikakhulukati eMelika, lebebayingabata.
Ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup , i-Europe iyahola nga-10-6
I-Europe itawutfola ligunya lelisetulu ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup ngemuva kwekucedza imidlalo yabo ngeMgcibelo ngemabhola lamane kanye nemachuba lamane, ibe seyincobe i-United States nga-10-6.
Umlingani lojabulisako Tommy Fleetwood naFrancesco Molinari bahola lomncintiswano ngekuncoba kabili Tiger Woods, lokwaholela ekutseni leLe Golf National ibe nemaphuzu lamane.
Licembu laseYurophu laThomas Bjorn, lebelifuna kubuyisa indondo lebeyilahlekile eHazeltin eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile, lalicinile kulicembu laseMelika lebeliphambanisa emidlalweni yemabhola lamane yasekuseni, lelihlula nga-3-1.
I-USA yabhekana kakhulu nalelive, yawina lemibili, kodvwa behluleka kuvala leliphutsa.
Licembu laJim Ferrick lidzinga emaphuzu lasiphohlongo emidlalweni lelishumi nakubili ngeLisontfo kute ligcine indondo.
Fleetwood nguye wekucala eYurophu kutfola emaphuzu lamane alandzelana, kantsi yena naMolinari, labatfola ligama lelitsi Mollywood ngemuva kwemaphelasontfo lamakhulu, baba ngulababili kuphela labatsatsa emaphuzu lamane emidlalweni yabo lemine yekucala emlandvweni weRyder Cup.
Ngemuva kwekubamba boWoods naPatrick Reid ngemagoli lamane, bahlangana kahle futsi bancoba umoya waWoods lowafa kanye ne-American rookie, Bryson DeChebmo, ngemagoli lamane.
Woods, lowaba nemidlalo lemibili ngeMgcibelo, bekakhombisa kukhatsateka lokukhulu, kepha nyalo sewulahlekelwe ngemidlalo lengu-19 ku-29 ngemabhola lamane, kantsi emabhola lamane  lasikhombisa alandzelana.
Justin Rose, lowaphumula emdlalweni wakhe wasekuseni we-four-ball, wabuyela ku-Henric Stenson, lowakhandza yena, wawina Dustin Johnson kanye naBrooks Keppke nga-2/1, lababili bebasezingeni lekucala kanye nalesibili emhlabeni.
EYurophu, lomdlalo awukasiwo luhambo lolulula nalolumnandzi lolunemalanga lasemini eningizimu-nshonalanga yeParis.
Emaphuzu lamabili latfolwa nguJordan Spieth kanye naJustin Thomas, labengemachawe katsatfu, ngeMgcibelo, aba ngumgomo wemaMelika.
Baphuma baphumelela ngekuphumelela lokukhulu nga 2/1 kulabase Spain bo John Ram na Ian Poulter emdlalweni wemabhola lamane, baphindze baphuma ngemuva kwesikhatsi, behlulwa ngu Poulter na Rory McIlroy nga 4/3 kuma-quarter, balahlekelwa ngemagede lamabili ekucala.
Kuvele kwaba kabili emlandvweni we Ryder Cup lapho licembu liphuma ngemuva ngemaphuzu lamane, liphuma lodwa, ngobe licembu la Ferrick, njengendvuna, bekudzingeka kutsi lidlale umdlalo lofanako kute libambe indondo.
Nobe kunjalo, ngemuva kwemalanga lamabili anesikhundla sesibili, kuhlasela ngeLisontfo kubonakala shengatsi sekuphelile.
INyakatho Korea itsi angeke iyekele tikhali yayo ngaphandle kwekwetsembana
INdvuna Yetepolitiki yaseNyakatfo Korea yatsi kuNhlangano Yemave Emhlaba ngeMgcibelo kutsi lokuchubeka kwetibopho kukhulisa kungetsembi kweMelika nekutsi kute simo lapho live layo lingeke liyekele tikhali talo te nyukliya.
Ri Yong Ho watsi ku-General Assembly yemnyaka, i-North Korea itsatse "tinyatselo letitsite tekwenta lokuhle" kulomnyaka lophelile, njengekumisa kuhlolwa kwenyukliya kanye nemakhemikhali, kucedza indzawo yekusebenta yenyukliya kanye nekutinikela ekukhuliseni tikhali te-nuclear kanye nasekwakheni buchwepheshe be-nuclear.
"Kodvwa, asikaboni kuphendvula lokunebulungiswa lokuvela eMelika", washo.
"Ngaphandle kwekwetsembela eMelika, kute kuciniseka ngekuphepha kwetfu, futsi angeke sibe setimeni tekutsi sibe setimeni tekutsi sitibambe singakahlosi".
Nanobe Ri aphindze waveta kukhonona kwaseNyakatfo Korea ngekumelana neWashington 'nendlela yekucedza kukhicita imphi ngetigaba' lapho khona iNorth Korea itawuvuzwa ngekutsatsa tinyatselo letincane, lesitatimende sakhe besibalulekile ngobe besingasilahli sinye sikhatsi sekucedza kukhicita imphi ngaphandle kwekucondziswa, njengobe kwentiwe yiPyongyang esikhatsini lesengcile.
Ri wacaphuna sitatimende lesentiwa nguKim Jong-un kanye naDonald Trump emhlanganweni wekucala wemengameli waseMelika kanye nemholi waseNyakatfo Korea lowaba seSingapore ngaJuni 12; lapho Kim atsembisa kucala inchubomgomo yekucedza kusebentisa i-nuclear kuleyo ndzawo, kantsi Trump watsembisa i-North Korea kutsi itawuba nesiciniseko sekuphepha.
INyakatfo Korea ifuna kucedza iMphi yaseNingizimu neNyakatfo yeKorea nga-1950-53, kepha iMelika itsi iPhenyani kumele ivele iyekele tikhali yayo te nyukliya.
I-Washington iphindze iphikise ticelo tekwehlisa tijeziso leticinile temave emhlaba leticondziswe eNyakatfo Korea.
I-US icindzetela kutsi kususwe ema-nuclear, futsi ikhulisa umfutfo wayo ngetindlela tetinhlawulo kute ikhone kucinisekisa kutsi imphi seyiphelile, kusho Ri.
Umcondvo wekutsi tijeziso tingasibeka phansi, ngumcabango longasiyo yetintfo bantfu labangati kutsi sibangani.
Kodvwa inkinga lenkhulu kutsi kucindzetelwa lokungapheli kucinisa kungetsembi kwetfu.
Ri akazange akhulume ngenchubomgomo yemhlangano wesibili wa Kim na Trump, lowabekwa ku-UN ekucaleni kwaleliviki.
Esikhundleni saloko, lomengameli wacaphela imihlangano lemitsatfu emkhatsini waKim kanye nemholi waseNingizimu Korea, Moon Jae-in, etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile, futsi wengeta watsi: Kube iNingizimu Korea, hhayi iMelika, beyiyingxenye yaloluhlelo lwekucedza kusebentisa i-nuclear, ngabe akukabi khona kucedza kusebentisa i-nuclear.
Nanobe kunjalo, indlela labekhuluma ngayo beyehluke kakhulu kuloko labekusho emhlanganweni we-UN General Assembly ngemnyaka lowengcile ngesikhatsi atsi kushaya i-raket yaseNyakatfo Korea eMelika bekungeke kugwenywe ngemuva kwekutsi Mengameli Trump abite Kim ngekutsi "ngumbulali wetikhali".
Kulomnyaka, eUN, Trump, lowetsembisa kubulala iNyakatfo Korea ngalokuphelele emnyakeni lowengcile, wancoma Kim ngekutitsatsa kwakhe matima tindlela tekucedza tikhali, kepha watsi kunyenti lokusamele kwentiwe, futsi tijeziso kumele tihlale tisekhona kuze iNyakatfo Korea icedze tikhali.
NgaLwesitsatfu, Trump watsi kute sikhatsi lafuna kusicitsa: "Kungenteka kutsatse iminyaka lemibili, lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu, akunandzaba".
I-China neRussia bacabanga kutsi Umkhandlu Wekuphepha Wemave Emhlaba kumele ukhutsate iPhenyango ngetinyatselo letitsetfwe.
Nanobe kunjalo, Mengameli waseMelika Mike Pompeo, wakhuluma eMkhandlwini weTekuphepha we-UN ngeLesine watsi: "Lokufakwa kwetibopho nguMkhandlu weTekuphepha kumele kuchubeke ngekutimisela futsi ngekuciniseka kuze kube ngulapho sesibone kucedvwa ngalokuphelele, lokugcwele futsi lokucinisekisiwe kwekusebentisa imphi yemandla langasiwo enyukliya".
Umkhandlu weTekuphepha wacinisa tijeziso teNorth Korea kusukela nga-2006 ngenhloso yekuvimba Pyongyang kutsi isekele tinhlelo tayo tetinyukliya kanye netibhobho.
Pompeo wahlangana naRi ngesikhatsi semhlangano we-UN General Assembly, wase utsi utawuvakashela iPhenyans futsi ngenyanga letako kute alungiselele umhlangano wesibili.
Pompeo uvakashele iNorth Korea katsatfu kulomnyaka, kodvwa luhambo lwakhe lwekugcina aluphumelelanga.
NgaJulayi, washiya iPhenyang atsi kukhona lokwentiwako, kodvwa ema-awa lambalwa ngemuva kwekuhamba kwakhe, iNorth Korea yamlahla ngekumcela kutsi ente tintfo letitsite.
INyakatfo Korea yetsembisa emhlanganweni lowabanjwa ngenyanga leyengcile, kutsi itawubhidlita loluhlelo lwekusakata imikhumbi yetindiza kanye neluhlelo lwekusakata imikhumbi yenyukliya uma ngabe iMelika itsatsa tinyatselo letifanele.
Ngekusho kwakhe, Kim wamtjela kutsi "tindlela letifanele" labekhuluma ngato nguleti ticinisekiso tekuphepha Trump labetetsembise tona eSingapore kanye netinyatselo tekucinisa budlelwane neWashington.
Bafundzi baseHarvard bafundza kuceceshwa
Kufundza lokusha lokwetfulwe kuHarvard kulomnyaka, kusite bonkhe bafundzi labasebancane kutsi bafundze kulala kancono futsi balwe nemasiko ekudlisa bantfu i-caffeine kute bahlale baphapheme.
Lomunye umfundzi wemfundvo watfola kutsi bafundzi labaphumelelako emhlabeni bavame kungati kutsi bangativikela njani.
Charles Chesler, longuphrofesa wetemphilo yekulala eHarvard Medical School kanye nalosebenta eBrigham and Women's Hospital, wente luhlelo lalukholelwa kutsi lwekucala lolunjalo eMelika.
Ngemuva kwekutfola loko, wacala wacabanga ngalendzaba, wacala ngekwetfula umbiko mayelana nekungalali kahle kanye nekungasebenti kahle kwekusebenta.
Ngesikhatsi ngicedza kukhuluma, intfombatana yeta kimi yatsi: "Ngiyacolisa kutsi angikaze ngikuve loku, ngobe sengitawucedza kufundza".
Watsi kute umuntfu lowake wamtjela ngekubaluleka kwekulala, lokwangimangalisa kakhulu", washo njalo lomake kuThe Telegraph.
Lesifundvo lesicala kufundvwa bafundzi kulomnyaka, sichaza kutsi imphilo yekulala kahle iyasita njani ekufundzeni kanye nasetintfweni temidlalo, kanye nekutsi kuyasita njani kutsi utive kahle.
Paul Barreira, longuphrofesa wetemphilo yengcondvo eHarvard Medical School kanye nemcondzisi lomkhulu we-University Health Services, utsi lelivesi lafuna kufundzisa bafundzi ngemuva kwekutfola kutsi bafundzi bebangalali kahle ngesikhatsi seliviki.
Lesikolwa sitsatsa li-awa linye, futsi bafundzi benta imisebenti leyehlukene.
Lenye incenye yaloluhlelo ichaza likamelo lelisendlini yekulala, lapho bafundzi bafundza khona ngekushaya tinkomishi tekubhakela, emakhethini, ema-exercise kits kanye netincwadzi, batfole lwati mayelana nekutsi lemisebenti kanye naletinye tintfo letibangela kuphelelwa butfongo - lokufaka ekhatsi ikhofi, kukhanya - kuletsa njani imiphumela yetemidlalo, kanye nekutsi kubaluleke kangakanani kulala kahle malanga onkhe.
Kulenye incenye, bafundzi bafundza ngekutsi kulahlekelwa butfongo sikhatsi lesidze kungakhulisa ematfuba ekushaywa yinhlitiyo, kuhlatshwa sitilondza, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Luhla loluhlanganyako lwendzawo yekuhlangana, lukhutsata bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngemphilo yabo yamalanga onkhe.
Siyati kutsi loku ngeke kusente sishintje indlela lesiphila ngayo.
Kodvwa sicabanga kutsi banalo lilungelo lekwati, njengabo bonkhe bantfu, kutsi kubhema kuyitsintsa njani imphilo yabo", kwengeta Phrofesa Chesler.
Utsi, "Loku kutigcabha lokungamanga ngekusebenta busuku bonkhe kusolo kugcwele, futsi buchwephesha bakamuva kanye nekucindzeteleka kwebafundzi kukwenta kube yinkinga kutsi ungalali".
Utsi, kulala kahle lokwenele "sibhamu semfihlo" semfundzi sekulwa nekucindzeteleka, kuphelelwa ngemandla kanye nekukhatsateka, ngisho nekulwa nekukhuluphala, ngobe kungakhoni kulala kahle kwenta ingcondvo yakho ihlale ilambile.
Raymond Saw, umfana loneminyaka lengu-19 lohlala eCalifornia lofundza ngekwakheka kwebantfu, wasita Phrofesa Chesler ekwakheni luhlelo lwekuhlola, ngesikhatsi ahambela kulelinye leliklasi emnyakeni lowengcile ngesikhatsi aseHarvard.
Watsi lesifundvo samvula emehlo futsi samkhutsata kutsi asakatele lwati lwakhe kulo lonkhe likhampasi.
Lenye intfo lafuna kuyenta kutsi bonkhe bafundzi bafundze ngalendlela ngaphambi kwekutsi bangene kulesinye sifundvo.
Phrofesa Chesler utjela bafundzi kutsi bafake ema-alamu labayala bantfu kutsi balale futsi bavuke, futsi akhumbule kutsi kukhanya kwe-LED kanye ne-electronic screen kuyingoti futsi kuyayiphazamisa indlela umuntfu lalala ngayo.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Umgoli waMenga uletsa kuncoba ngelicembu laGerard
I-Ranger yabhekana nalenye ingoti ngesikhatsi igoli yaDolly Meng ibulala licembu laSteven Gerrard lelingakahlanganiswa naleli lelashaya i-Livingston nga-1:0.
Licembu le-Ibrocks belitsemba kutfola inzuzo yalo yekucala ngemuva kwe-4-1 kuSt Johnstone ngaFebhuwari, kodvwa licembu laGary Holt labulala Gerrard emidlalweni lengu-18 njengemphatsi, lesala ngemuva ngemaphuzu lasiphohlongo, liniketa likilabhu le-Hearts, lelibhola le-Scottish Premier League, kuncoba lokulula.
Menga wafaka umgoco ngemizuzu lesikhombisa ngaphambi kwekuphela kwemdlalo, futsi i-Ranger, lebeyicindzeteleke kakhulu, beyingasafuni kucedza lomdlalo.
Ngesikhatsi iRanger seyehlele esigabeni sesitfupha, iLivingston seyihle yafika esigabeni sesitsatfu, bese yehlulwa yiHibernian kuphela ngekuholwa kwemagoli.
"Rangers" kungenteka babe netinkinga letengetiwe ngemuva kwekutsi umgwebi welibhola Calum Spence, aphatfwe sifo sekuhlukunyetwa ngemuva kwekutsi intfo letsite iphonswe esigabeni setivakashi.
Gerrard wabamba tikhundla letisiphohlongo eqenjini lelidlula e-Eire laya kuma-semi-final e-Scottish League Cup.
Holt, yena, usebentisa indlela lefanako naleyo lebeyisetjentiswa nguLevy 11 ngesikhatsi achubeka nekubhekana naHarts kuleliviki leliphelile, futsi utawujabula kubona indlela labambelele ngayo.
"Rangers" kungenteka bebayimphumelelo ngekuphatsa inkemba, kodvwa "Livingston" beyisebentisa kakhulu uma ibhola seyifike kubo.
Bebalindzeleke kutsi bente umgomo ngemuva kwemizuzu lemibili, ngesikhatsi Mengele atsatsa sipho sekucala ku-Scott Pittman, lesasivinjelwe ngu-Alan McGregor, kodvwa lomdlali wasemuva wasebentisa litfuba.
