Umjovo lomusha wekugoma lomdlavuza ungafundzisa umtimba wemtimba kutsi ubone emaseli lakhula kabi bese uyawabulala
Incenye yekwelapha kwaleligciwane kutsi lifundzisa umtimba wemtimba kutsi ubone emagciwane langekho emtimbeni.
Lendlela ikutsatsa emaseli emtimba wekugoma kumuntfu logulako bese awashintja endzaweni yekugoma.
Ngenca yalolushintjo, lamangcolane akwati kubona loluhlobo lweprotheni lebonakalako kumdlavuza, bese kufanele abuyiselwe.
Umutsi wekugoma losetjentisiwe uveta imiphumela lemihle kubantfu labanetinhlobo letehlukene temdlavuza.
Lomunye logulako lowatfola lomjovo, futsi lonemphilo lehlantekile lebeyifundze kubona emagciwane langakavami, sekuphele tinyanga letingu-18 kutsi lomdlavuza wehlise emagciwane.
Lendlela yekwelapha isebentisa emagciwane emtimba kutsi atsatfwe kumuntfu logulako bese ayashintjwa etitfolakale etitfweni letiphilako, bese lamagciwane ayabona i-HER2 leyakhiwe ngetinhlobo letinyenti temdlavuza, bese lamagciwane ayaphindze afakwe kumuntfu logulako.
Phrofesa Jay Berzofsky, we-National Cancer Research Institute eBethesda, eMaryland, utsi: "Lemiphumela lesesiyitfolile iveta kutsi sesineligciwane lelisembili lelihle kakhulu".
Phrofesa Berzofsky uyachaza: HER2  ivuselela kukhula kwetinhlobo letinyenti temdlavuza, lokufaka ekhatsi umdlavuza welibisi, wema-ovari, wemaphaphu kanye newekuhlanyela.
Indlela lefanako isetjentiswe ngekuphumelela ekwelapheni sifo se-leukemia, ngekutsatsa emagciwane emtimba wemuntfu bese uwafundzisa kutsi angamelana njani nemagciwane emdlavuza.
