I-HIV/AIDS: EmaShayina Abika Kukhula Kwema-14 Ephesenti
I-China imemetele kwandza lokungu-14 ekhulwini kwebantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS.
Ngekusho kwebantfu labatiphetse, bantfu labangetulu kwa-820 000 kulelive banato letifo.
Emnyakeni wesibili wa-2018 kuphela, kwavela emacala lamasha lacishe abe ngu-40 000.
Liningi letigameko letinsha letenteka tibangelwa kuhlangana kwebulili, lokukhombisa kutsi loku akukabi njalo.
Ngekwesintfu, i-HIV isakateka ngekushesha etindzaweni letitsite eChina ngenca yekumpontjelwa ingati lenesifo.
Kodvwa-ke, lokungenwa yi-HIV ngalendlela sekucishe kwehle, kusho tikhulu tetemphilo tase-China emhlanganweni lobewuse Yunnan.
Linani lebantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS eChina lenyuka ngeminyaka lelikhulu.
Kudluliselwa kwe-HIV ngekwelicansi kuyinkinga lenkhulu emmangweni we-LGBT wase-China.
Bungqingili bavalwa eChina nga-1997, kodvwa kucalisa kwebantfu labangaboLGBT kusatfolakala kabanti.
Lucwaningo lukhombisa kutsi ngenca yemagugu lahlala njalo kulelive, 70-90% walabadvuna labanabo labadvuna bagcina bashade nalabasikati.
Esikhatsini lesinyenti, lokutfolakala kwaletifo kubangelwa kutsi labantfu labasikati labasebancane abavikelekile.
Kusukela nga-2003, hulumende wase China wetsembise kutsi utawuletsa imitsi lelapha iHIV kubo bonkhe bantfu njengencenye yemitamo yekulwa nalenkinga.
