Noma kunjalo, lomuntfu lonemehlo lamnyama, lobekabukeka njengengwenya, Johnny English, watfola lilungelo lakhe lekuba yingoti kwesibili.
Umlingisi, vele, ngumuntfu loyimfihlo longumuntfu longakwati kwenta lokutsite, nanobe atsi uhleti kahle, utfola lokuncane kwa Clouseau, tinhlobo teMnumzane Bean kanye nencenye yalomfana lowenta linotsi linye emculweni weChariots of Fire e-London ngemnyaka wa 2012 ngesikhatsi semicimbi yekuvula i-Olympics.
