Yini i-Global Citizen Festival futsi ngabe ikhona yini leyentile kute kuncishiswe buphuya?
NgaMgcibelo, i-Global Citizen Festival itawubanjwa eNew York, umcimbi wemculo weminyaka yonkhe lofaka ekhatsi licembu lelikhulu le-star-band, lelitawuphindze libe nemsebenti lofanako - kucedza buphuya emhlabeni wonkhe.
Umnyaka wesikhombisa, umkhosi we World Citizen Festival uhlanganisa bantfu labatinkhulungwane letinyenti e Central Park, hhayi nje kuphela kute bajabulele kuhlabela kwa Janet Jackson, Cardi B na Sean Mendes, kodvwa futsi kute bacoce ngenhloso yawo - kucedza buphuya lobukhulu ngemnyaka wa 2030.
Umkhosi weBantfu Bemhlaba, lowacala nga-2012, uchubeka nemklamo wemhlaba wonkhe wekulwa nebuphuya, lochutjwa licembu le-International Human Rights Watch, lelinematsemba ekucedza buphuya ngekukhulisa linani lebantfu labalwa nabo.
Kute utfole lithikithi lelihle (uma ungakatsandzi kukhokha lithikithi le-VIP), kufanele ube wente umsebenti wekutinikela nobe utfumele umholi wemhlaba i-imeyili, ushayele lucingo nobe wente lokutsite lokutsite lokutsite lokunemsebenti lokwentiwa kute kukhuliswe kwatiwa kwemgomo wakho wekucedza buphuya.
Kodvwa-ke, umcimbi we-Peace Citizens Festival ube yimpumelelo kangakanani kuleminyaka lengu-12 leyendlulile mayelana nekutfola umgomo wawo?
Ngabe lomcondvo wekunika bantfu umvuzo ngekutsi bahambe bayohlala emikhosini yabo, ucinisekisa kutsi bantfu bayakhona kwenta loko, nobe kumane nje kungulenye yetindlela tekwenta bantfu bacabange kutsi bente umehluko ngekubhalisa sitatimende nobe ngekutfumela imilayeto ku-Twitter?
Labasunguli be-Global Citizen batsi kusukela nga-2011 sekube netinhlelo tekuhlanganyela letitigidzi letingu-19 letentiwe ngulabo labatsandza umcimbi, labaphishekela tinhloso letehlukene.
Ngenca yaloko, baholi bemhlaba batsembise kutfola imali lengetulu kwa-R370 billion, letawutsintsa timphilo tebantfu labangetulu kwa-2.25 wetigidzigidzi nga-2030.
Ekucaleni kwa 2018, lelicembu lakhipha tigwebo letingu-390 kanye netimemetelo letentiwe ngenca yaloko lelakwenta, lokungenani tigidzigidzi letingu-10 temadola sekakhokhiwe nobe tivele tihlengiwe.
Lelicembu lilinganisela kutsi lemali leniketwe bantfu isite bantfu labacishe babe tigidzi letingu-649 emhlabeni wonkhe.
Lenye yetintfo letibalulekile lesetentiwe, lebitwa ngekutsi ngu The Power of Nutrition, ngumhlangano wase UK webatsengisi kanye nebasebenti labatsandza kusita bantfwana kutsi bakwati kwenta lokunyenti, batsembise kunika iRwanda tigidzi temarandi letingu 35 kute kusitwe kucedza kungondleki esifundzeni sabo, ngemuva kwekutfola ema-tweet langetulu kwa-4 700 avela kubantfu labatsintsekako ku-Global Citizens.
"Ngekusekelwa nguhulumende wase-UK, banikeli, bohulumende betive kanye ne-Global Citizens njengawe, singenta kutsi kungalungi kwemphakatsi mayelana nekungondleki kube yintfo leyenteka kadzeni", kusho umnisi we-Power of Nutrition, Tracy Ullman, ngesikhatsi sekugidza kwakhe lokwentiwa eLondon nga-Apreli 2018.
Lelicembu liphindze latsi ngemuva kwekwenta lokungaba ngu-5000 lokuncenga i-UK kutsi yente ncono kudla kwebantfwana nabomake, hulumende wamemetela kutsi utawufaka sandla ku-Power of Food, lokutawuhlanganisa bantfwana nabomake labatigidzi letisihlanu ngetintfo letitsite letihlose kwenta ncono kudla.
