I-USA ingasebentisa imikhumbi yemanti kutsi ivimbele kutfunyelwa kwemandla eRussia: Indvuna Yetepolitiki
INdvuna yeLitiko leTasekhaya laseMelika, Ryan Zinke, itsi iWashington ingasebentisa imikhumbi yayo yemanti uma kudzingeka, kute ivimbele ema-Russian energy kutsi angenele timakethe, lokufaka ekhatsi iMphumalanga Lesekhatsi.
Zinkke utsi kuba khona kweRashiya eSiriya, ikakhulukati lapho isebenta khona ngekumenywa nguhulumende losemtsetfweni, kuyindlela yekufuna emakethe lensha yemandla.
"Ngicabanga kutsi sizatfu lesenta kutsi babe khona eMiddle East kutsi bafuna kutsengisa emandla agezi ngendlela lefanako naleyo labayenta ngayo eMpumalanga yeYurophu, eningizimu yeYurophu", kwasho yena.
Lesikhulu satsi kunetindlela tekusombulula lenkinga.
"Umbuso waseMelika, kanye nemabutfo etfu, unemandla ekuvikela indlela levulekile yemikhumbi, futsi uma kudzingeka, ungavimba emandla awo kutsi angafiki emakethe", kusho lomphatsi.
Zinkke ukhuluma nebahlanganyeli bemcimbi lohlelwe yiConsumer Energy Alliance, licembu lelingasebenti ngekutsengisa lelitibita ngekutsi 'livi lebasebentisi bemandla' eMelika.
Uphindze acatsanise indlela yase Washington yekubukana neRussia ne Iran, atsi iyafana.
"Lisu letemnotfo lase-Iran nase-Russia" "kusebentisa nekusebentisa kabi uphethiloli", kusho lomphatsi, abita iRussia ngekutsi "yindzawo lenemachinga" lenemnotfo lotsembele kumoya.
Letimemetelo betivame kwentiwa ngenca yekutsi hulumende waTrump ubeke umgomo wekukhulisa kutfunyelwa kwegesi lemenyiwe eEurope, esikhundleni seRussia leniketa lokungabizi kakhulu kubatsengi base Europe.
Ngenca yaloko, tiphatsimandla te-Trump Administration, kufaka ekhatsi umengameli wase-USA Donald Trump, betama kucinisekisa iGermany kutsi iphume kulomklamo longakalungi we-North Stream-2, lowenta iBerlin ibe "sitfunjwa" seMoscow, ngekusho kwaTrump.
I-Nord stream-2 lebeyibita tigidzigidzi leti-11 temadola, lebeyifuna kuphindzaphindza emandla ekushayela lambili, kuze kube ngemakhilomitha-ngcobe latigidzigidzi leti-110 eMoscow, beyisolo ibekwa njengentfo lezuzisa umnotfo.
I-Kremlin itsi kuphikiswa lokukhulu kwe-Washington kwalomklamo kubangelwa tintfo tetemnotfo futsi kuyindlela yekuncintisana lokungakafaneli.
Ngiyacinisekisa kutsi siyavumelana ngekutsi emandla angeke abe lithuluzi lekucindzetela nekutsi batsengi kumele bakhone kukhetsa labatsengisa , kusho iNdvuna yeMandla eRussia Alexander Novak ngemuva kwekuhlangana naNdvuna yeMandla yaseMelika Rick Perry, lokwenteka ngeNyoni eMoscow.
Lesimo seMelika sabangela kuphendvuka kweJalimane, leyafakazela kutsi iyavumelana nalomklamo.
Bakhiciti baseJalimane, labamelele i-BDI, bacele i-USA kutsi ihlale khashane netimiso te-EU tekuphakelwa kwemandla kanye netivumelwano te-Berlin ne-Moscow.
"Nangabe umbuso wesitsatfu ungena emandleni etfu, loko kubeka inkinga lenkhulu", kusho Dieter Kempf, umholi weBundesverband der deutschen Industrie (BDI), ngemuva kwekuhlangana lokusha kwa Angela Merkel, umengameli waseJalimane, kanye naVladimir Putin, umengameli waseRussia.
Umlingani weMalta, Elizabeth Warren, utawufundza ngekucophelela kutsi angangenela yini umhlangano webuMengameli wanga-2020
Elizabeth Warren, losenate waseMassachusetts, watsi utawucabangisisa ngekukhetsa kwakhe kutsi utawuba ngumengameli ngemuva kwelukhetfo lolutawuba semkhatsini.
Emhlanganweni welidolobha e-Holiocka, eMassachusetts, Warren wacinisekisa kutsi utawucabanga ngekuncintisana.
"Sikhatsi sekutsi bafati baye eWashington futsi balungise hulumende wetfu lodzabukile, futsi kute bente loko, kudzingeka bafati kutsi babe ngetulu", kusho Warren The Hill.
Ngemuva kwaNovemba 6, ngitawucabangisisa ngekukhetsa umengameli.
Warren watsi: "Ucondzisa lesigodzi endleleni lengakafaneli".
"Ngikhatsateke kakhulu ngaloko Donald Trump lakwentako elubanjweni lwetfu lwentsandvo yelinyenti", kwasho yena.
Warren usihlambalatiso lesivulekile saTrump kanye nemuntfu lofuna kuba nguMengameli wemajaji aseNingizimu Afrika, Brett Kavanaugh.
Ku-Twitter yakhe ngaLesihlanu, Warren wabhala: "Yebo, kufanele sihlolisise i-FBI ngaphambi kwekutsi sicale kuvota".
Nanobe kunjalo, lucwaningo lolwentiwe ngaLesine lukhombisa kutsi Warren yena akacabangi kutsi kufanele akhetse kubusa nga-2020.
Ngekusho kweluphenyo lwe-Suffolk University/Boston Globe Political Research Center, ema-58% ebantfu labangavota eMassachusetts batsi umengameli akukafaneli akhetse.
Ngalokwehlukile, emaphesenthi lamashumi lamatsatfu nakubili ebantfu labatsintsekako basekela letinhlelo takhe.
Luhlolo lukhombisa kutsi bantfu basekela Deval Patrick, lobekangumbusi, nga-38% lofuna kutsi angenele lukhetfo, kantsi 48% akafuni.
