Biden utsi utawenta sincumo sekubaleka ngaJanuary, kusho i-Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ukhuluma nge-PTSD yaTrick Palin emhlanganweni wa Donald Trump
Track Palin, loneminyaka lengu-26 budzala, wajoyina libutfo lemasotja ase-Iraq ngemnyaka wa-September.
Waboshwa futsi wabekwa licala lekushaya lomunye umuntfu emakhaya ngeMsombuluko ebusuku.
"Indvodzana yami ibuyele ekhaya, futsi seyihlangabetana netimo letifanako naleto letihlangabetana nemindeni lehluphekile futsi lelimatekile, kantsi nemasotja etfu abuya avuliwe", kusho yena emhlanganweni wakhe na Donald Trump eTulsa, e-Oklahoma.
Palin wabita kuboshwa kwakhe ngekutsi "yintfo lebuhlungu" wase ukhuluma ngendvodzana yakhe kanye nalabanye bantfu labake baphila emphini, watsi: "Bayabuya sebagucuke, batibuta kutsi ngabe baphatfwa ngenhlonipho leyenele yini, njengebasebenti, emasotja, tindiza kanye naletinye tisebenti tasemphini".
Track Palin waboshwa ngeMsombuluko eWasillah, eAlaska, wabekwa licala lekushaya lomunye wesifazane ngekuhlanganyela naye, kanye nekugcwala, ngekusho kwaDan Bennett, lomele Litiko leMaphoyisa laseWasillah.
Emave langu-18 kanye neDistrict of Columbia, avumelana nalenchabhayi yemgomo lomusha wekufuna kukhuseliswa
Emave langu-18 kanye neDistrict of Columbia basekela kucabana lokusha kwemtsetfo waseMelika lovimbela kuvikelwa kwebantfu lababalekile nobe labahlukunyetwa emakhaya.
Ngekusho kwe-NBC News, bameleli betifundza netigodzi letingu-18 bafaka umbiko weseluleko senkantolo eWashington DC ngeLisihlanu mayelana nekwesekela umceli wekukhosela lobekafakaza kutsi lomtsetfo awusebenti.
Ligama leliphelele lemmangali ecaleni laGrace v. Sessions, lelifakwe yi-American Civil Liberties Union nga-Agasti, lelimelene nemitsetfo yahulumende, alichazwa.
Lomake utsi indvodza yakhe lengumhlali kanye nemadvodzana akhe labadlala indzima yelicembu lebugebengu bamhlukubeta, kodvwa ngaJulayi 20 tiphatsimandla taseMelika tamlahla.
Wabanjwa eTexas.
Bameli bemtsetfo baseveni labasekela Grace batsi i-El Salvador, iHonduras neGuatemala bafaka ticelo letinyenti tekukhosela eMelika, njengobe emave labhekana netinkinga letisakateke kakhulu tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwebugebengu kanye nekuhlukunyetwa emakhaya.
Inchubomgomo lensha yekukhosela yaseMelika icitsa sincumo lesentiwa yi-Immigrant Appeals Council nga-2014 lebesivumela bantfu labangenabo bufakazi lababalekela budlova basekhaya kutsi bafake sicelo sekukhosela.
Umshushisi lomkhulu waseDistrict of Columbia, Karl Racine, watsi enkhulumeni yakhe lelandzelako "ayibuki emashumi eminyaka yekusebenta kwemtsetfo wahulumende, wahulumende kanye newemave emhlaba".
Umtsetfo wavelonkhe udzinga kutsi tonkhe ticelo tekukhosela tihlolwe ngekulandzela emaciniso kanye netimo taloko lokushiwo, futsi loku kwephula lomtsetfo, kusho umeluleki wetemtsetfo.
Bameli baphindze batsi umtsetfo wekungavumeli bantfu labangena e-United States ulimata umnotfo wase-United States, baphindze batsi bantfu labangephansi kwalesigaba sebantfu ngibo labatsandza kuba bosomabhizinisi futsi babasita kutsi babe nemisebenti.
NgaJuni, umshushisi lomkhulu Jeff Sessions wayala emajaji kutsi angasabaniki indzawo yekuhlala bantfu labahlukunyetwa ngekuhlukunyetwa emakhaya nobe bantfu labadvuna.
"Lesigaba sitawuniketa labo labaphunyulako ngenca yekushushiswa nobe kwesaba ngenca yebuhlanga, inkholo, buve, nobe licembu lepolitiki", kusho Sessions esitatimendeni sakhe sangamhlaka 11 Inhlaba.
Lelithulusi belingakaze lihlelwe kutsi lisombulule tonkhe tinkinga, ngisho naletinkhulu kakhulu bantfu labahlangabetana nato onkhe malanga emhlabeni wonkhe.
