Bantfu labasindze kuleyo nhlekelele bebabeketelela.
"Kumatima kakhulu nyalo", kusho make waRisa Kusuma loneminyaka lengu-35 budzala, ngesikhatsi advudvuta umntfwana wakhe losagulako endzaweni yekukhosela edolobheni lelibhujisiwe lasePalu.
"Ematiko etemphilo atfola bantfu labalimele njalo ngemzuzu.
Emanti lahlobile aswelekile.
Bantfu bayabuyela emakhaya abo labhujisiwe, bagubha tintfo letimanti futsi betama kusindzisa nobe yini labangayitfola.
