Labanye balabo labalimala, kufaka ekhatsi Dwy Harris, lobekahlukunyetiwe ngumgogodla kanye nemhlane, bebakhe eceleni kwesibhedlela semasotja ePalu, lapho tigulane betitfola khona kwelashwa ngaphandle, ngobe baphocelelwa kutsi bashiye indzawo ngenca yekunyakatisa lokukhulu lokwenteka.
Uyakhala nakakhumbula kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwabhubhisa likamelo lakhe lehhotela lelisesitezi sesihlanu, lapho bekuhlala khona nemkakhe nendvodzakati yakhe.
Kute sikhatsi sekusindzisa.
Ngatsi ngitsi ngishaywe ngumoya, Harris watjela i-Associated Press, wachaza kutsi umndeni wakhe ufike edolobheni kutewugubha umshado.
Ngeva umkami akhala acela lusito, kwase kuba khona kuthula.
