INdvuna yaseMelika isola iChina ngekuhlaselwa ngemaphromoshini
Ngemuva kweliviki linye linye linye lelinye laphephabhuku lelisemtsetfweni lase China liphehlelele likhangiso lelikhasini lemine kulelinye liphephandzaba laseMelika lelichaza tinzuzo tekutsengisa emkhatsini we US ne China, liBambela lase US eChina latisola iBeijing ngekusebentisa emaphephandzaba ase America ekusakazeni inkhulumo.
Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump, ngeLwesitsatfu, wacaphuna i-Des Moines Register China Daily, liphephandzaba lelikhulu le-Iowa, lapho akhuluma khona ngekungenela kwalelive lelisesha elukhetfweni lwe-Congress, lolutawuba ngaNovemba 6.
