Bantfu labanyenti labakhulu labatsandza litiko le-Republican bakhetsa kuhlala bangekho futsi basekela umcashi we-Supreme Court, Brett Kavanaugh, nanobe sekunetinsolo letinyenti tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi.
Lusizi lwendzaba lwaba lukhulu, futsi linyenti lebantfu labaseRiphabliki labamemetela ngalokusemtsetfweni kutsi bafuna kuchubeka nekuvota.
Akukafaneli ubuyele kuloko, "kubhala Grant Rieher, longuphrofesa wetembusave e-Maxwell School eSirakusa University, esihlokweni sakhe lesishicilelwe ngeMgcibelo.
Rier ukhatsateka kutsi kutama kwaSenator Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) kwenta luphenyo lwe-FBI lolwentiwe emzuzwini wekugcina, kutawuncedza kucedza lulaka lwebavoti.
"Bafati angeke bakukhohlwe lokwentekile itolo, angeke bakukhohlwe kusasa noma ngeLweti", kusho Karin Jean-Pierre, umeluleki lomkhulu kanye nesikhulumi savelonkhe se-MoveOn, ku-Washington, D.C.
NgaLesihlanu ekuseni, bamemeta batsi: "Novemba uphambi kwetfu!" ngaphandle kweSigungu saVelonkhe, ngesikhatsi emaRiphabliki lalawula liKomiti leTemtsetfo ancuma kukhetsa Kavanaugh, nanobe bekunebufakazi baDokotela Christine Blasey Ford, kusho i-Mic.
"Inshisekelo yentsandvo yelinyenti kanye nekugcugcutelwa kwayo kutawudlulela ngalokungekho emtsetfweni", kusho Stu Rotenberg, losati setembusave lesingahambisani nelicembu.
