Umuntfu lowasungula iWebhu uhlela kusungula i-Internet lensha ye-Google ne-Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, losungula iWeb, usungula inkapani lefuna kuchudzelana ne-Facebook, i-Amazon ne-Google.
Umklamo wekugcina waloluhlelo loludvumile, i-Inrupt, yinkampani lesekelwe ku-solid-based open source.
Solid ivumela basebentisi kutsi bakhetse kutsi bangayigcina kuphi imininingwane yabo nekutsi bangayivumela kubani.
Ku-Fast Company, Berners-Lee utsi injongo ye-Inrupt kutsi abe ngumbusi wemhlaba.
"Kufanele sikwente nyalo", kusho yena mayelana nekusungula kwakhe.
"Lona ngumzuzu losemlandvweni".
Loluhlelo lusebentisa buchwepheshe be Solid, lobuvumela bantfu kutsi bakhe ema-POD abo.
Lencwadzi ingafaka ekhatsi emarekhodi ebantfu lochumana nabo, ema-account, likhalenda, umtapo wemculo, naletinye tintfo lotisebentisako kanye naletisetjentiswa emsebentini wakho.
Isebenta ngendlela lefanako ne-Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack kanye ne-Spotify  konkhe kungasetjentiswa kusiphequluli sinye ngesikhatsi sinye.
Lokwenta sitoko setfu setinombolo singakhetseki kutsi silawulwa ngumuntfu, futsi singatfola nobe nguyiphi imininingwane lesiyidzingako.
Le-Company ibita lomgomo ngekutsi "kucinisa umuntfu ngemininingwane".
Ngekusho kwa-CEO John Bruce, umcondvo we-Inrupt kutsi inkapani inikete imitfombolusito, tinchubo kanye nemakhono lafanele kwentela kwenta iSolid itfolakale kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Nyalo le-company ifaka ekhatsi i-Berners-Lee, i-Bruce, i-IBM leyayitsenga le-security platform, kanye ne-volunteer developer community.
Kusukela kuleliviki, bakhi betinsita emhlabeni wonkhe batawukwati kwakha tinhlelo tabo tekusebentisa emandla lavela ku-Inrupt.
Berners-Lee watsi yena nelicembu lakhe abakakhulumi ne-Facebook ne-Google mayelana nekutsi ngabe inkampani yakhe kufanele yini yente tingucuko letinkhulu letitawugucula imodeli yabo yebhizinisi ngalokuphelele ngalobunye busuku.
"Asikaticeli timvumo tabo".
Kulesitfombe sakhe lesishicilelwe ngeMgcibelo, Berners-Lee wabhala kutsi umsebenti we-Inrupt kutsi unikete emandla etekuhweba kanye netinhlelo tekuvikela bucotfo kanye nekhwalithi yenethiwekhi lensha leyakhiwe ku-Solid.
Nga-1994 Berners-Lee wagucula i-Internet ngekwakha i-World Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Kuletinyanga letilandzelako, livi la-Berners-Lee belikhuluma kakhulu mayelana nekungatingeni etintfweni letitsite.
Ngisho nangesikhatsi asungula i-Inrupt, Berners-Lee utawuhlala angumsunguli kanye nemcondzisi we-World Wide Web Consortium, i-Internet Foundation kanye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Nginelitsemba lelikhulu mayelana nalelikhaya le-Internet letako", kusho Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: sisebenti seliSontfo lesatfola iSichu Victoria ngesikhatsi seMphi yeLive Yekucala
Emlandvweni weSontfo laseNgilandi, ngumunye kuphela umfundisi lowanikwa umchele waVictoria ngesikhatsi semphi yelive yekucala, futsi loku kwaboniswa edolobheni lakubo eminyakeni lelikhulu leyalandzela.
Umholi welicembu le-Veterans, uMfundisi Bernard Vann wanikwa lomklomelo mhlaka 29 Septemba 1918 ngekuhlanganyela ekuhlaseleni iBellenglish neLeyukur.
Lokubuhlungu kutsi, wabulawa ngumuntfu lobekabulala bantfu ngemasotja ngemuva kwemalanga lamane, angakaze atfole umklomelo lomkhulu waseBrithani.
Lesikhumbuzo lesisikhumbuto salomcimbi savulelwa ngemadvodzana akhe lamabili emkhosini weRushden, eNorthamptonshire, ngeMgcibelo.
