Ngekusho kweliphephandzaba i-London Gazette, lelakhokha mhlaka 29 Septemba 1918, Pholonkhulu Vann wahola libutfo lakhe lemasotja lalihamba ngephansi kweSihosha saseSt.
Ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, wagucuka waya emgceni wekulwa, wahola licembu ngemandla lamakhulu, wase uphonsa sikhali sakhe ngesandla sinye, wabulala emasotja lamatsatfu.
Vann wabulawa ngumuntfu lobekabulala emaJalimane nga 4 October 1918, lokwacishe kwaba yinyanga ngaphambi kwekuphela kwemphi.
Umtukulu walomlingisi, Michael Vann, loneminyaka lengu-72, watsi angeke akhone kwenta intfo lenjalo, kodvwa loko kuyamcinisa.
