Wacala kudlala ngemnyaka wa 1997 eWalterram, lapho licembu lebeliholwa nguSeverjano Ballesteros, belinemaphuzu lasihlanu ekuhola kunaleli laseMelika, kepha belibambe kancane lelicembu, laphumelela ngemaphuzu langu-141⁄2- 131⁄2.
"Uyachubeka nekukhumbuta kutsi besinelinani lelikhulu eWalterram, besinelinani lelikhulu eBrooklyn lapho silahlekelwe khona, futsi besinelinani lelikhulu eWalterram lapho siphumelele khona, kodvwa kuze kube ngunyalo", kusho Bjorn, lowatfolakala kulendzaba ngemuva kwekubuka liClass of 2018, abaleke kuLe Golf National, abaphumelele nga-5-3 boLesihlanu nangoLesitfupha, lokwenta kutsi kube nemiphumela lelishumi naku-6.
Ngako-ke, umlandvo utawufakazela kutsi loku akusiko kuphela.
Kusasa utawucala kusebenta ngalokuphelele.
Hamba uyokwenza lokuhle.
Kute lokwentekako kuze kube ngulapho sekubekwe emaphoyinti.
Kunemgomo, futsi lomgomo litfuba lekutsi sitfole indondo, futsi nguloko lokufanele sikugcine engcondvweni.
Ngikhulume ngekucophelela, ngigcile kulabadlali betfu labangu-12, kodvwa siyati kutsi simelene nani - simelene nalabadlali labakhulu emhlabeni.
Bjorn wancoma badlali bakhe ngekutsi bakhone kudlala indzima yabo etindzaweni letingenamsebenti, watsi: "Bengingeke ngikhone kudlala kahle kakhulu kunaloko lengikwentako.
Kusasa sitawuhlangabetana neluhlolo lolwehlukile.
Kusasa kutawucala kucocisana ngemuntfu ngamunye, futsi loko kuhlukile.
Kujabulisa kakhulu kuba nebangani nawusebenta kahle, kodvwa nawusebenta wedvwa, utfola emandla akho onkhe njengengcweti yegalufu.
Nguloko kanye lokudzingeka kutsi kubonakale kubadlali kute nabo bakhone kutikhandla.
Umlingani wakho usala ngemuva futsi naye kufanele ente konkhe lokusemandleni akhe.
Ngalokwehlukile kuBjorn, umlingani wakhe, Jim Ferrick, ukholelwa kutsi badlali bakhe batawenta kancono kunalabo labadlala nabo, ngaphandle kwaJordan Spit naJustin Thomas, labatsatsa emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulalamane.
Ferik yena wacedza lomncintiswano wekugcina, waba yincenye yelicembu lelahlula eBrooklyn, ngaphambi kwekutsi alahlekelwe yimphela ngesikhatsi iEurope ibamba umcimbi we "Miracle in Medina".
"Ngikhumbula onkhe emagama labhalwe ngalendzaba", kusho yena, aphendvula umbuto mayelana nekutsi Ben Crenshaw, longumphatsi welibhola lemidlalo nga-1999, wahlanganisa njani badlali bakhe ngaphambi kwelilanga lakhe lekugcina.
Kusasa sinemidlalo lemikhulu lelishumi nakubili, kodvwa nani niyafuna kuyicedza masinyane, njengobe kwenta iBrooklyn, njengobe kwenta iMedina.
Nangabe lomdlalo ucala kuhamba ngendlela yinye, loko kubeka umfutfo lomkhulu kumdlalo losemkhatsini.
Sesivele sihlele kahle umdlalo wetfu futsi sibeke labadlali ngendlela lesicabanga kutsi ilungile, futsi kusasa sitawuzama kwenta imilingo.
Thomas wanikwa umsebenti wekwetama kuhola lomncintiswano, wahlangana naRory McIlroy emdlalweni lomkhulu lowawuhlangene na Paul Casey, Justin Rose, John Ram, Tommy Fleetwood na-Ayan Poulter kanye nalabanye badlali baseYurophu labasezingeni lelisetulu.
"Ngikhetse licembu lelifana naleli, futsi ngilihlelele ngendlela lengiyitsandzako, ngobe ngibona kutsi ngalendlela batawuvala tonkhe tintfo letingaba nemaphutsa", kusho Bjorn, nakakhuluma ngekukhetsa kwakhe kwebadlali.
Kwetfulwa kabusha kwemkhumbi lomusha wemphi waseJalimane
Le-Frigate yakamuva yeMikhumbi yaseJalimane beyilindzeleke kutsi isebente nga-2014 kute itsatse sikhundla semikhumbi yemphi lebeyigugile ngesikhatsi seMphi yeBandze, kepha loku angeke kwenteke ngemnyaka lotako ngenca yetintfo letingasebenti kahle kanye nekukhula kwemali, kubika i-Local Media.
I-Rhineland-Palatinate, umkhumbi lomkhulu we-Baden-Württemberg, nyalo sewutawusebenta kuze kube yinyanga yekucala ya-2019, kusho i-Die Zeit ngekucaphuna kummeleli wemphi.
Lomkhumbi bekumele ujoyine imikhumbi ngemnyaka wa 2014, kepha tinkinga letenteka ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa kwato, kwabangela kutsi kube matima.
Letikebhe letine teBaden-Württemberg, letatsengwa ngemnyaka wa 2007, titawufaka esikhundleni semikhumbi leseyigugile ye Bremen.
Kuyatfolakala kutsi titfombo letinjalo titawuba nemshayasibhamu lonemandla, tinhlobonhlobo tetindiza letingaphasi kwemhlaba kanye netinhlelo tekulwa nemikhumbi, kanye naletinye tindlela tekusebentisa ema-steels, njengekunciphisa kusebenta kwe-radiolocation, infrared kanye ne-acoustic signatures.
Letinye tintfo letibalulekile kufaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze sekusebenta  kumele kube nekwati kutfumela emafregat lamasha sikhatsi lesingaba ngeminyaka lemibili khashane nemaphothi asekhaya.
Nobe kunjalo, kucedvwa kwekusebenta lokungapheli kusho kutsi imikhumbi yemphi lesetulu, lekutsiwa isita iJalimane kutsi isakatele emandla ayo kulamanye emave, itawuphelelwa sikhatsi nasetjentiswa, kusho i-Die Zeit.
Le F125 lebeyiyindzawo lenkhulu yekuphepha, yavela etinhlokweni temilandvo emnyakeni lowengcile, ngesikhatsi le German Navy ivele yavala kutsi le F125 isebente futsi yabuya nayo eBlohm & Voss e Hamburg.
Loku kwaba kwekucala lapho khona imikhumbi ibuyiselwa emuva ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa.
Bekungatiwa lokuncane ngetizatfu tekubuya, kepha ema media aseJalimane abhekisa kulokunye lokumatima kwe software kanye ne hardware lokwenta kutsi le nkhumbi lengasiyo yetemphi ingasebenti.
Letinkinga teluhlelo betibaluleke kakhulu, njengoba imikhumbi yelicembu le Baden-Württemberg itawusetjentiswa ngemalunga emkhumbi lalikhulu nemashumi lamabili  kuphela ihhafu yemandla emsebenti kumafrigate lamadzala ase Bremen.
Ngetulu kwaloko, bekubonakala kutsi lomkhumbi unesisindvo lesikhulu, lokwenta kutsi ungabi nemandla futsi loko bekwenta kutsi umkhumbi weMikhumbi Yetemphilo ungaboni kutsi ungahle uhlehliswe njani esikhatsini lesitako.
Kubonakala kutsi lenkhumbi lenemathani langu 7000 i-Rheinland-Pfalz, inesisindvo lesiphindvwe kabili kunesikhumbi lesasisetjentiswa ngemaJalimane emphini yesibili yemhlaba.
Ngaphandle kwemishini lephukile, kubita kwemsebenti wonkhe kufaka ekhatsi kucecesha licembu, nako kuyinkinga.
Kutsiwa seyifinyelele kuma-euro latigidzigidzi leti-3.1 (ema-dollar latigidzigidzi letingu-3.6) ngetulu kwema-euro latigidzigidzi leti-2.2 ekucaleni.
Tinkinga tekugcina imikhumbi lemisha itfwele timphandze tibaluleke kakhulu ngenca yeticwayiso letisandza kwentiwa mayelana nekuncishiswa kwemandla emkhumbi waseJalimane.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, longumholi welikomidi lelivikelako lephalamende yaseJalimane, wavuma kutsi emabutfo emphi "aphelelwe ngemabutfo" langakhona kuwatsatsa.
Lesikhulu satsi inkinga seyibhebhetekile ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi ngobe imikhumbi lendzala beyisusiwe, kepha kute imikhumbi lebeyifakwa esikhundleni sayo.
Wabubula ngekutsi kute ngisho namunye umkhumbi lowakhona kutsi usetjentiswe ngemkhumbi.
I-National Trust isilalela imfihlo yemabhatata
Lucwaningo lolusha lolwentiwe endzaweni lesetindzaweni letiseTihoscotland, lufuna kukhombisa kutsi emalulwane asebentisa njani lendzawo kute afune kudla.
Sinelitsemba lekutsi lolwati lolutfolakale lutasisita kutsi sifundze lokunyenti mayelana nendlela letilwane letinemaphiko letiphila ngayo futsi tisisite nasetindzabeni tekulondvolota tilwane.
Lolucwaningo loluhlelwe bososayensi baseScotland, lutawuhlola ema-lobster, ema-soprano, kanye nemabata lamadze lanoboya kanye nema-Dobanton night herons, lahlala e-Inverewe Gardens, eWester Ross.
Emagilasi lakhetsekile atawufakwa etindzaweni letitsite letisedvute nalelikhaya kute kubonwe kutsi lamagundvwane ahamba njani kulo lonkhe leliviki.
Basebenti be-NHS kanye nemavolontiya batawenta luhlolo loluhambako, basebentisa tintfo tekubona letisetjentiswa ngesandla.
Kuhlolisisa lokwentiwe ngulososayensi kutawukhombisa kutsi kukhala kwawo kukhala kangaki kanye nekutsi nguwaphi emalunga lahlukahlukene lawenta imisebenti yawo.
Ngemuva kwaloko, kutawentiwa ibalave lendzawo yekuhlala bese kwentiwa umbiko kute kubonakale kahle kutsi tilwane tiphila njani.
Rob Dewar, losekela umeluleki we-NTS, utsi letintfo letitfolwe titokhombisa kutsi nguyiphi indzawo lebaluleke kakhulu kubologwaja nekutsi isetjentiswa njani nguletinye tilwane.
Lolwati lutakusita kutsi ubone tindlela letinkhulu tekunakekela indzawo, njengekwakha emadlelo, kanye netindlela tekugcina emahlatsi asezingeni lelikahle lebatfish kanye naletinye tilwane letihlobene nato.
Emashumi eminyaka lendlulile, linani lemadlangala eScotland nase Britain liyehla kakhulu.
Tiyesaba kulahleka ngenca yekwakhiwa nekutfutfukiswa kwetindzawo letihlala kuto kanye nekulahleka kwendzawo letihlala kuyo.
Imishini yekukhanyisa umoya kanye netintfo tekubasa tingenta tintfo letiyingoti, njengekubamba tinhlanti, kusebentisa emakhemikali ekwakha kanye nekutingela timvu.
Ecinisweni, emalulwane akaboni.
Noma kunjalo, indlela yato yekubamba ebusuku yenta tindlebe tato tibe lusito kakhulu kunemehlo awo nakubanjwa inyama.
Tisebentisa tindlela letinkhulu tekubona kutsi ngukuphi lokuyinsayeya endleleni.
I-NTS, lelawula takhiwo temlandvo letingetulu kwa-270, tivande letingu-38 kanye nemahekitha langu-76 000 emhlaba eveni lonkhe, itsatsa tindzaba tekuba khona kwemabhatata ngalokubanti.
Le-ejensi inebantfu labalishumi labaceceshiwe labatiphatsa kahle, futsi labahlale benta luhlolo, kuhlolwa kanye nekusindziswa.
Le-WUA yaze yavula indzawo yekucala yekugcina emalulwane eScotland, eThreave Estate leseDumfries naseGalloway, lapho khona kuhlala khona tilwane letisiphohlongo kuletingu-10.
David Thompson, umphatsi welitiko letindlu, utsi lendzawo iyindzawo lekahle yekuhlala.
"Lapha eTheave, yindzawo lenhle kakhulu yekubhukusha", washo.
