Kodvwa kunyenti lesingakawati ngalemikhomo, ngako umsebenti lesiwenta lapha naletinye tindzawo utasisita kutsi sicondze kahle kutsi yini ledzingekako kute iphile kahle.
Uphindze akhumbute kutsi kubalulekile kuhlolwa kwemalulwane ngaphambi kwekwenta umsebenti wekunakekela etindzaweni letitsite, ngobe kubulala lidada linye kungaholela ekubulaweni kwemalulwane lamakhulu lamane kanye nemantfombatana, kantsi kungenteka kubulale bonkhe bantfu.
Emalulwane avikelwe ngumtsetfo, futsi kubulala, kuhlukubeta nobe kucedza indzawo lehlala emalulwane akukavumeleki.
Elizabeth Ferrell, losisebenti lesisebenta eScotland lesisebenta nge-Bat Conservation Foundation, ucela lusito emphakatsini.
Utsi: "Kusekunengi lokusamele sikufundze ngemabhatata etfu, futsi asati kutsi tiphila njani tinhlobo letinyenti tawo".
