Brexit: UK uya isola ngemakhi wemoto lalahlekelwe phakadze
INdvuna yeBhizinisi neBhizinisi, Greg Clark, itsi iBrithani "itawuzisola ingunaphakadze" uma ngemuva kwe-Brexit ilahlekelwa sikhundla sayo sekuba ngumholi wemhlaba wekukhicita timoto.
Waphindze waphawula ngetindzaba letitsi iToyota UK itjele iBBC kutsi uma iUK ingaphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, itawuyekela kukhicita esiteshini sayo eBernaston, edvute nase Derby.
"Sidzinga kutsengiselana", kusho Mnu. Clark.
Umkhicito wetimoto waseJapan utsi umonakalo lobangelwe kubambezeleka emnyeleni uma ngabe kungaphumeleli kucedza umsebenti.
Lelihhovisi lase Bernaston likhicita iToyota Auris ne Avensis, futsi ngemnyaka lophelile lakhicita timoto letingu 150 000, 90% wato tatfunyelwa kulamanye emave e-European Union.
"Ngicabanga kutsi uma iBrithani ishiya i-EU ekupheleni kwenyanga yeNdlovulenkhulu, umkhicito utawuyekela", kusho Marvin Cook, umphatsi we-Toyota eBernaston.
Labanye bakhiciti betimoto base UK bakhulume ngetinkinga tekuphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano sekuhweba nemave ngemave, kufaka ekhatsi iHonda, iBMW kanye ne Jaguar Land Rover.
Sibonelo, iBMW itsi itawuvala sikhungo sayo seMini eOxford kungakapheli inyanga ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Lokukhatsateka lokukhulu kutsi, ngekusho kwebakhiciti betimoto, uma ngabe kute sivumelwano se-Brexit, tinhlelo tekuphakela titawufakwa engotini lenkhulu.
Umgca wekukhicita weToyota ucala kusebenta ngesikhatsi lesifanele, kantsi tincenye temoto letentelwe bantfu tiyatfolakala ku-UK naku-EU njalo ngemizuzu lengu-37.
Uma i-UK ingaphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano nga-March 29, kutawuba netinkinga emnyeleni, lokusho kutsi labosomabhizinisi batawuchubeka nekubambezeleka futsi kube nekushoda kwetincenye tekusebenta.
Le nkampani itsi iToyota angeke ikhone kugcina tintfo letisele kulelihhovisi layo leDerbyshire sikhatsi lesidze, ngako-ke itawuyekela kukhicita.
Mnu Clark watsi luhlelo lwa Theresa May lwebudlelwane be-EU, lolwatfolakala ku-Checkers, "luye lwatfutfukiswa kute kugwenywe lokuhlolwa kwemincele".
"Sifuna kutsengisa. Sifuna kutsengisa lokuncono kakhulu, lokungavumeli kutsi, ngiphindze ngitsi, singaphumeleli nyalo kuphela, kepha siphindze sisebentise lelitfuba esikhatsini lesitako", washo ku BBC Radio 4 ku "Today".
"Akusiyo iToyota kuphela, kepha nalabanye bakhiciti batsi kufanele sikhone kuchuba tinhlelo tekuphakela letinemphumelelo".
I-Toyota ayikhoni kuchaza kutsi itawuyekela nini kukhicita, kepha icwayisa ngekutsi esikhatsini lesidze, letindleko letengetiwe titawunciphisa kukhicita kwefektri futsi ekugcineni tiholele ekunciphiseni imisebenti.
Peter Tswalalis, losebente iminyaka lengu-24 eBernaston futsi lowengamele inhlangano yetisebenti, utsi kukhatsateka kwalabasebentisi kuyakhula: "Ngekubona kwami, uma singalahlekelwa ngemisebenti, angeke sikhone kuyibuyisa".
Lomkhulumeli wahulumende utsi: "Sente luhlelo lolucondzile nalolunemandla lolutawuba khona macondzana nebudlelwane betfu ne-EU".
Umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein ungahle ucitselwe eceleni, ngekusho kweNdlu LemiBuso
Umhlangano wa Donald Trump nalokhetsiwe weNdvuna yeTemtsetfo Rod Rosenstein ungahle ucitselwe kulelinye liviki njengobe kuchubeka umzabalazo wekukhetfwa kwaBritt Kavanaugh kutsi abe lijaji lelikhulu, kusho iWhite House ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein uphetse umsebenti wemeluleki lobalulekile Robert Mueller, lophenya kungenelela kweRussia elukhetfweni, budlelwane emkhatsini webasiti baTrump neRussia kanye nekungenelela kwemtsetfo lokungaba khona kumengameli.
Kungakholwa kwa Trump kutsi angamsusa yini esikhundleni lesengamele umshushisi lomkhulu, lokwenta kutsi kungabi nekutetsemba kwa Mueller, bekusolo kuhlupha bantfu labanyenti eWashington tinyanga letinyenti.
Ekucaleni kwalenyanga, i-New York Times yabika kutsi Rosenstein ucoce ngekusetjentiswa kwetindzaba letibhalwe nguTrump kanye nekungenela kwakhe ngekulandzela sichibiyelo semashumi lamabili nesihlanu.
Rosenstein uyaphika kutsi loku kuliciniso.
Kodvwa ngeMsombuluko lowengcile, waya eNdlini leMhlophe kutsi ayokwetfula sitatimende sekwesula kwakhe.
Esikhundleni saloko, bekutawubanjwa umhlangano waTrump ngeLesine, lobekahlala e-UN eNew York.
Trump watsi angatsandza kumcosha Rosenstein, kodvwa lomhlangano wahlehliswa kuze angahlangani neKomidi yeTemtsetfo yeSigungu saVelonkhe lapho khona Kavanaugh kanye nalomunye wabomake labamsola ngekumhlukubeta, Dokotela Christina Blasey Ford, bebabeka bufakazi.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump wayala kutsi kwentiwe luphenyo lweliviki lonkhe mayelana netikhalo te-FBI nga Kavanaugh, lokwabambelela kakhulu ekuvoteni lokugcwele eSenate.
Sarah Sanders, longumkhulumeli waTrump, ukhulume ku Fox News ngeLisontfo.
Watsi nakabutwa kutsi utawuhlangana yini naRosenstein, waphendvula watsi: "Sikhatsi sekuhlangana asikatenti, mhlawumbe kuleliviki, kepha kungenteka kutsi sitawubekwa ngemuva kweliviki linye ngenca yetintfo letenteka enkantolo lephakeme".
Kodvwa-ke, ngitsandza kutsi emaphephandzaba akwati loko.
Labanye batfumeli betindzaba bayaphikisana nalombiko: Sanders akazange aphindze abambe tinkhulumo eNdlini leMhlophe kusukela ngaSeptemba 10.
Umsakati Chris Wallace wabuta kutsi kungani.
Sanders utsi kungatfoli tinhlangano tekubika tindzaba akubangelwa "kunyembenyeka kwemphakatsi" wetintsatseli te-TV, nanobe atsi: "Ngingeke ngiphike kutsi badlala indzima yebantfu".
Wetsembisa kukhulisa kuchumana emkhatsini waTrump nebetindzaba.
 Umengameli ubambe imihlangano leminyenti, aphendvule imibuto yetintfumi kunanobe ngumuphi lomunye umengameli ngaphambi kwakhe,  wengeta, kepha akazange akhulume ngenombolo:  Sinetibalo.
Sanders utsi letinkhulumo titawuchubeka, kodvwa nangabe labomabhizinisi bakhona kubuta umbusi weMelika umbuto, loko kungaba ncono kunekukhuluma nami.
Senta njalo kanyenti, futsi uyati kutsi singakhi tinkhulumo lesitichubele tona kulamasonto lambalwa lendlulile, kantsi nangabe ukhuluma nemengameli waseMelika matfupha, loko kungaba yindlela lekahle yekubita labamemeteli.
