Jean Freeman, we-MSP, wabhalela tisebenti takhe lencwadzi kungakapheli tinyanga letisitfupha ngaphambi kwekutsi i-UK iphume ku-EU.
Hulumende waseScotland sewuvele utibophelele kutsi utawufaka sicelo setindleko tekufaka sicelo setakhamuti te-EU letisebenta kuhulumende wato.
