Bantfu labasebenta nabo labasuka kulo lonkhe lelive lase-EU kanye nalamanye emave, bafaka ekhatsi emakhono laligugu lacinisa futsi entfutfukisa umsebenti wetemphilo, futsi bazuzisa tigulane nemiphakatsi lesiyisebentelako.
