Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami e-Indonesia
Ngekusho kwebamemeteli, lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 bashone ngekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami leyahlaselwa edolobheni lase-Indonesia iPalu ngaLesihlanu, futsi linani lebantfu labashonile kulindzeleke kutsi likhule.
Ngenca yekwehluleka kwetekuchumana, basindzisi abakwati kutfola lutfo ku Donggala, indzawo lesenyakatfo yePalu, lesedvute nendzawo yekutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla la-7.5.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-16 000 baphuma ePalu ngenca yalenthlekelele yemvelo.
Nati letinye tintfo letibalulekile ngaPalu naDonggala, leseSulawesi:
I-Palu  inhlokodolobha yesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, lesiseceleni kweligede lelincane elugwini lolusentshonalanga lwesichingi sase Sulawesi, linebantfu labangu 379 800 (ngemnyaka wa 2017).
Lelidolobha belisandza kugubha iminyaka lengu-40 likhona ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami.
Donggala  sifundza lesisemkhatsini wemakhilomitha lamakhulu lamatsatfu (180 miles) elugwini lolusenyakatfo-nshonalanga yeSulawesi.
Sifundza, indzawo yekuphatsa lencane kunesifundza, ngemnyaka wa 2017 besinebantfu labangu 299 200.
Kubamba timfishi kanye nekulima kusisekelo semnotfo wesifundza sase Central Sulawesi, ikakhulukati esifundzeni sase Donggala.
Umkhicito we nickel nawo ubalulekile emnotfweni walesifundza, kepha ugcwele eMorali, elugwini loluphambene neSulawesi.
Ngekusho kwe-Indonesian Disaster Management Agency, kuPalu naseDonggala sekube netinhlekelele letinyenti letakhishwa ngu-tsunami kuleminyaka lengu-100 leyendlulile.
Nga-1938, i-tsunami yabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-200 futsi yabhidlita emakhaya lamanyenti eDonggala.
I-tsunami nayo yahlasela insimu yase Donggala lese nshonalanga nga-1996, yabulala bantfu labangu-9.
I-Indonesia isendzaweni lenemlilo lokhashane kakhulu, futsi ivame kuhlushwa kutamatama kwemhlaba.
Nati letinye tetindzawo letinkhulu letake tazamazama futsi tabulala ematsunami kuleminyaka lembalwa leyengcile:
2004: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu elugwini lolusentshonalanga lwesifundza sase-Indonesia i-Acheh enyakatfo yeSumatra ngaDecember 26 kwabangela i-tsunami leyayitsintsa emave langu-14, leyabulala bantfu labangu-226 000 elugwini lweLwandle i-Indian, ngetulu kwehhafu yabo e-Acheh.
2005: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokulandzelanako kwahlasela lusentse lwaseSumatra ngasekupheleni kwaMashi kanye nasekucaleni kwa-Apreli.
Emakhulu ebantfu abulawa esihlengeni saseNyas, lesiselugwini lweSumatra.
2006: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla la-6.8 kwahlasela eningizimu ye-Java, lokuyisichingi lesinelinyenti lebantfu e-Indonesia, kwabangela i-tsunami leyatamatama ngaselwandle loluseningizimu, leyabulala bantfu labangu-700.
2009: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla la-7.6 kwenteka edolobheni lasePadang, lokuyinhloko-dolobha yaseSumatra leseNtshonalanga.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1100 bafa.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla la-7.5 kwahlasela sihlenge saseMentawai, lesiseSumatra, kwabangela kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungaba ngemamitha lalishumi, kwabhubhisa emadolobhana lamanyenti kwabulala bantfu labangu-300.
2016: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokuncane kwahlasela iPidi Jaya eAchehe, kwabangela kuhlukunyetwa kanye nekwesaba njengobe bantfu bakhumbula kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabhubhisa kakhulu nga-2004 kanye ne-tsunami.
Ngalesikhatsi, bekungekho tsunami, kodvwa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 bafa ngenca yekubhujiswa kwetakhiwo.
2018: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela sihlenge lesitsite lesivakashelwa e-Indonesia, iLombok, kwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, ikakhulukati enyakatfo yalesihlenge.
Kuhlaselwa kwalelive kwabhidlita takhiwo letinyenti futsi bantfu labanyenti labebakhona bashiywa phansi kwesikhashana.
