Umshushisi weTemacala ufuna kuniketa sigwebo sekufa lesingakavami kumuntfu lobanjiwe ngebugebengu lobentiwa eNew York.
Umshushisi waseNew York ufuna kujeziswa ngekufa kwaSayfullo Saipov, losolwa ngekuhlaselwa kweNew York City lokwabulala bantfu labasiphohlongo  sigwebo lesingavamile lesentiwa ecaleni lelibekwe nguhulumende kusukela nga-1953.
Nga-Okthoba, Saipov, loneminyaka lengu-30 budzala, bekatsi wacasha iloli le-Home Depot kute ahlasele indlela yekugibela emabhayisikili eWestern Side Highway lese Lower Manhattan, acedza bantfu labahamba ngetinyawo kanye nebagibeli bemabhayisikili.
Kute kutfolakale kutsi sigwebo sekufa sifanelekile, bameli bemacala kumele bakhombise kutsi Saipov "wabulala" bantfu labangu-8 "walimata" labanye bantfu, ngekusho kwesatiso sekufuna kumbulala lesikhishwe eSouthern District yase New York.
Ngekusho kwemaphepha elicala, lamacala lamabili angahle ente kutsi sigwebo sekufa sikhokhelwe.
Emavikini lambalwa ngemuva kwalokuhlasela, lijaji lelikhulu lafundzela Saipov sigwebo lesinemaphuzu langu-22 lafaka ekhatsi emacala lasiphohlongo ekubulala ngenhloso yekuhlukunyetwa, lokuvame kusetjentiswa batekucala bahulumende bahulumende emacaleni ebugebengu lobuhlelekile, kanye nelicala lekusebentisa budlova nekubhubhisa timoto.
Ngekusho kwebashushisi, lokuhlasela "kwakuhlelekile futsi kuhloswe kahle" futsi Saipov wakufeza "ngendlela leyenyanyekako, lenesibindzi kanye nebugebengu".
Saifullo Habibullayevich Saipov wabangela kulimala, umonakalo kanye nekulahlekelwa emindenini kanye nakubangani baDiego Enrique Andjelini, Nicholas Clevés, Ann-Lora Decatt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlia, Ernan Ferrucci, Ernan Diego Mendoza kanye na-Alejandro Damiano Pagnuckko,  kusho satiso setinhloso.
Laba labasihlanu labafa bekubavakashi lababuya eArgentina.
Sekuphele iminyaka lelishumi umshushisi waseNingizimu yeNew York afuna kufa ngesizatfu selicala lelibi.
NgaSeptemba 2009, umbekwacala Khalid Barnes watfola sigwebo sekufa kwebantfu lababili labatsengisa tidzakamiva, kepha wagcina atfole sigwebo sekuhlala aphila.
Kugwetjwa kwekucala lokwentiwa ecaleni lelibekwe yinkantolo yase New York kwaba nga-1953 kuJulius na-Ethel Rosenberg, labashadikazi lababulawa ngeminyaka lemibili ngaphambilini ngenca yekuhlangana kwabo ngekuhlola emave ase Soviet Union ngesikhatsi semphi lebandzako.
BoRosenberg babulawa ngesitulo lesinemandla ngaJuni 19, 1953.
Ngekusho kwemiculu yeNkantolo, Saipov, lowatalwa e-Uzbekistan, akazange akhombise kucoliseka ngemuva kwekuhlasela.
Emaphoyisa atsi watjela baphenyi kutsi uyajabula kutsi wente njalo.
Ngekusho kwelicala, Saipov watjela tiphatsimandla kutsi wavuselelwa kubuka i-video ye-ISIL elucingweni lwakhe.
Waphindze wacela kutsi kubekwe ifulegi le-ISIL egumbini lakhe lasesibhedlela, kusho emaphoyisa.
Uphika tonkhe tizatfu letingu-22 tekumangalelwa.
David Patton, longulomunye webameli be-Federal Public Defenders, lowasekela Saipov, watsi "bakhatsateke kakhulu" ngesincumo se-SAPS.
"Sikholelwa kutsi sincumo sekushaya umuntfu esikhundleni sekumfaka ejele imphilo yakhe yonkhe ngaphandle kwekukhululeka, kutawenta buhlungu lobukhulu kakhulu kubo bonkhe labatsintsekako", kusho Patton.
Umvikeli waSaipov wavele wacela kutsi bangasifuni sigwebo sekufa.
LIPHAMULA le-Tory litsi NIGEL FARAJ akukafaneli abe nemtfwalo wekutsatsa tinyatselo tekwehlukana ne-EU
Emhlanganweni weTori lamuhla, Nigel Farage wetsembisa kutsi utawuletsa "libutfo lebantfu".
Lomholi wangaphambilini we-Ukip watsi bosopolitiki kumele "bativa banconota" bantfu labangafuni kucondza ku-Europe, njengobe lomunye webahlali be-parliament, Theresa May, asho kutsi yena kumele abhekane netingcoco ne-EU.
Lilunga lelicembu lemaConservatives, Peter Boone, watsi eBirmingham, iBrithani ngabe seyivele "ihambile" kube Mnu Farage bekangumbhalisi we-Brexit.
Nanobe kunjalo, inkinga May lahlangabetana nayo etama kuhlanganisa emacembu akhe lahlukene, iyachubeka ngekuhlanganiswa kwemalunga e-Tory Party laphikisana nekuPhuma kwe-EU emicimbini leyehlukene yekumelana ne-Brexit.
Lomengameli wetama ngalokusemandleni akhe kugcina lelicembu lakhe lelingumlingani, lakhuluma ngalo eChekers ngesikhatsi kuhlaselwa bantfu labatsandza iBrexit, labaphikisana nayo kanye ne-EU.
Labatsandzanako bayamcela kutsi achubeke etama kwenta sivumelwano neBrussels, nanobe kunemiphumela lemibi, kute ente labo labangavumelani ne-European Union kanye ne-Labour bakhetse emkhatsini waloluhlelo lwakhe kanye nekungahlaliseki.
Mnu. Boone watsi emhlanganweni we-Leave Means Leave eSolihall, ufuna "kubheja emaCheckers".
Waphindze wacela kutsi Mnu. Farage ahlanganyelwe futsi abekwe kutsi abambe lichaza leticondziso letibhekiswe eBrussels.
"Kube bekangumholi, ngabe sesivele siphumile", kwasho yena.
Lilunga le-Wellingborough laphindze latsi: "Ngitawuchubeka nekusekela i-Brexit, kodvwa kufanele siyincobe i-Checkers".
Akhuluma ngekumelana ne-EU, watsi: "Asikayi emphini yemhlaba kute sisebente.
Sifuna kubeka imitsetfo yetfu kulelive letfu.
Bowen walahla imibono yekutsi umbono webantfu sewushintjile ngemuva kwevoti yanga-2016: "Lisho kutsi bantfu baseBrithani bashintjile futsi bafuna kuhlala, akusilo liciniso".
Andrea Jenkins, losekela i-Brexit welicembu le-Tory naye bekakhona emhlanganweni, waphendvula batfumeli betindzaba watsi: "Ngitsi: Ndvunankhulu, lalela bantfu".
 Checkers akatemukeleki emphakatsini, kuphikiswa ngeke kuvote kulenhlelo, akatemukeleki ngisho nasemkhatsini wemalunga elicembu letfu kanye nebasebenti betfu, labavele bahlasele emigwacweni futsi bakhetse tsine kucala.
Ngicela nimise eceleni labantfu labatsite labatsite bese nilalela loko labakushoko.
Ekhuluma kuNksz May, wengeta watsi: "BoNdvunankhulu bahlala emsebentini wabo uma nje bahlala betsembekile etetsembisweni tabo".
Mnu. Faraj watsi uma ngabe bosopolitiki bafuna kutsengisa sincumo lesitsetfwe ku-referendum yanga-2016, kumele bente "kuva buhlungu".
"Manje sekuyindzaba yekwetsemba emkhatsini wetfu, bantfu, kanye nelicembu letembusave", utsi.
"Benta konkhe lokusemandleni abo kute bangayekele iBrexit, futsi lamuhla silapha kute sibatjele kutsi angeke sikhululeke.
Akhuluma nesive lebesimangele, watsi: "Ngifuna kutsi licembu letfu lepolitiki, lelisemkhatsini wekuphuma kwe-Brexit, lati kutsi liyakhatsateka.
"Sitawuhlanganisa emabutfo esive lasiphe inzuzo yekuncoba iBrexit, futsi angeke siyekele kudzimate kube ngulesikhatsi sibe sive lesimele, lesinemandla futsi lesitigcabhako".
Ngasona leso sikhatsi, labo labaphikisana ne-Brexit bahamba ngemgwaco e-Birmingham, ngemuva kwaloko baba nemhlangano wema-awa lamabili edolobheni.
Bantfu labambalwa bebabambelela kulokuvukela, baphakamisa emaphephadzaba labamemetela kutsi "Tori uyamelana ne-Brexit" kuleliviki.
Ngesikhatsi kuvulwa lomhlangano, lilunga lelicembu le Labour, Lord Adonis, wagceka emacembu langabamemeteli ngenca yetinkinga tekuphepha ku-app yelicembu.
"Laba bantfu batsi bangakwenta i-IT yabo kanye ne-Canada plus plus, basebente eminyeleni, bakhiphe emabhizinisi ngaphandle kwemincele ne-Ireland", kwengeta yena.
