Ngekucaphuna kumininingwane yelitiko leleningizimu, Park Byung Seug watsi, uma kucatsaniswa netigameko leti-2706 tekubaleka letabhalwa nga-2011, lelizinga liyehla laya ku-1127 emnyakeni lowengcile.
