Donald Trump, umengameli waseMelika, wacala ngekubeka umtselo ekucaleni kwalomnyaka etintfweni letitsite letitsengwa ngaphandle eChina, kufaka ekhatsi emagetsi elanga, insimbi kanye ne-aluminium.
