Umbiko wekugcina we-Florida Fish and Wildlife Commission ukhombisa kwehla lokukhulu kwelizinga le-red tide kuletinye tindzawo taseTampa Bay.
I-FWC itsi tindzawo letise Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte nase Collier tibiketela ngekuba khona kwetimbali letinyenti, lokukhombisa kwehla kwelizinga letigciwane.
iRed Tide isukela enyakatfo yePinell kuya eningizimu yeLee County.
Letindzawo letinkhulu tibonakala emavikini lalishumi kusuka elugwini lwaseHillsboro, kepha tincane kakhulu kunaleto letake tabonwa kuleliviki leliphelile.
Lolu lwandle lusha nalo luyatfolakala ePasco.
Kuleliviki leliphelile, kunekugcwala lokumaphakathi ePinellas County nasendzaweni lesedvute nayo, kunekugcwala lokuncane kuya etulu eHillsboro County ngaselwandle, kunekugcwala lokukhulu eManatee naseSarasota nasetigodzini letisemnceleni, kunekugcwala lokumaphakathi eCharlotte County, kunekugcwala lokumcoka eLee County ngaselwandle, futsi kunekugcwala lokumncane eCollier County.
Etigodzini tasePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, naseCollier, kusengenteka kutsi kube khona kuhlushwa kwetifo temoya.
Enyakatfo-nshonalanga yeFlorida, bekungekho lokwabitwa ngalendzaba ngeliviki leliphelile.
